e%20than%20150%20people%20have%20died%20in%20the%20violence%20and%20properties%20worth%20thousands%20of%20crores%20in%20the%20Imphal%20valley%20were%20looted%20and%20reduced%20to%20ashes.%20It%20will%20take%20many%20years%2C%20and%20perhaps%20generations%2C%20to%20overcome%20the%20trauma%20inflicted%20by%20the%20violent%20mobs%20and%20the%20state%20police.%20Even%20if%20peace%20returns%2C%20no%20Kuki%20will%20be%20willing%20to%20move%20to%20the%20Meitei%20areas%20and%20the%20same%20with%20the%20Meiteis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20days%20of%20the%20conflict%20did%20appear%20like%20a%20violent%20outburst%20over%20the%20demand%20for%20the%20Schedule%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status%20by%20the%20Meitei%20community.%20However%2C%20over%20time%2C%20it%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20pre-meditated%20and%20planned%20conspiracy%20against%20the%20Kuki%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20previous%20conflicts%2C%20the%20recent%20violence%20has%20divided%20the%20state%20administration%2C%20the%20police%2C%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20bureaucracy%20deeply%20across%20ethnic%20lines.%20Under%20such%20circumstances%2C%20the%20rule%20of%20law%20and%20party%20affiliations%20appear%20to%20have%20taken%20a%20back%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20brutal%20incidents%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcrippled-in-mob-attack-kuki-bjp-mla-from-manipur-admitted-to-delhi-hospital%2Farticle66942275.ece%5C%22%3Emob%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thanlon%20MLA%20Vungzagin%20Valte%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-woman-killing-ethnic-violence-9-held-5-were-women-101689529607305.html%5C%22%3Ebrutal%20killing%20of%20a%20woman%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Sawombung%20area%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Imphal%20East%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1053615%2Fmanipur-violence-sc-says-there-has-been-absolute-breakdown-of-law-and-order-summons-dgp%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CMy%2520aunt%252C%2520a%2520Kuki%252D%2C%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520he%2520said%2520on%2520Twitter.%5C%22%3Ekilling%20of%20a%20lady%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20Undersecretary%20to%20the%20Government%20of%20Manipur%2C%20with%20her%20son%3B%20the%20looting%20and%20torching%20of%20Kuki%20homes%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20police%20personnel%20are%20testimonies%20to%20the%20State%E2%80%99s%20failure%20to%20control%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20politicians%2C%20including%20cabinet%20ministers%20and%20officers%20of%20the%20state%20and%20Union%20government%2C%20are%20so%20unsafe%2C%20it%20cannot%20be%20imagined%20how%20risky%20the%20life%20of%20the%20common%20man%20is%20in%20a%20situation%20of%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EState%20police%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20credibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20such%20compelling%20circumstances%2C%20ten%20Kuki%20MLAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nationalheraldindia.com%2Fnational%2Fkuki-mlas-afraid-of-travelling-to-imphal-likely-to-skip-assembly-session%5C%22%3Esubmitted%20a%20representation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20May%2012%2C%20demanding%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20administration%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20in%20the%20state.%20They%20expressed%20that%20they%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20government%20and%20the%20majority%20community.%20Thus%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20separate%20administration%2C%20which%20earlier%20was%20a%20demand%20put%20forth%20by%20militant%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20United%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(UPF)%20and%20the%20Kuki%20National%20Organisation%20(KNO)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-violence-kuki-zomi-mlas-separate-administration%5C%22%3Ehas%20become%20the%20demand%20of%20the%20Kuki%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%20represented%20by%20its%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2016%2C%20the%20MLAs%20further%20demanded%20that%20a%20separate%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(DGP)%20and%20Chief%20Secretary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-hill-kuki-zomi-mlas-dgp-chief-secretary%5C%22%3Ebe%20appointed%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately%20for%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%2C%20Pherzawl%2C%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Tengnoupal%20and%20Chandel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20plea%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20DGP%20and%20Chief%20Secretary%20posts%20is%20an%20urgent%20administrative%20necessity%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20intricately%20linked%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20separate%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20Kuki%20MLAs%E2%80%99%20representation%20to%20the%20Centre%20has%20also%20been%20the%20longstanding%20dream%20of%20Kuki%20militants%20over%20the%20last%2030%20years.%20There%20has%20never%20been%20a%20situation%20so%20conducive%20for%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20separate%20political%20entity%20as%20it%20is%20happening%20now.%20In%20their%20representation%2C%20the%20Kuki%20lawmakers%20told%20the%20Centre%20that%20the%20two%20communities%20living%20together%20as%20one%20would%20be%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20government%20employees%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community%20had%20to%20leave%20Imphal%20owing%20to%20the%20threat%20to%20their%20lives.%20Kuki%20bureaucrats%2C%20including%20senior%20IAS%20and%20IPS%20officers%2C%20posted%20in%20Imphal%20can%20no%20longer%20discharge%20their%20duties.%20They%20either%20took%20leave%20or%20relocated%20to%20safer%20places.%20There%20have%20been%20reported%20mass%20transfers%20of%20employees%20working%20in%20courts%20and%20government%20schools%2C%20as%20well%20as%20clerical%20staff%20in%20all%20offices.%20They%20are%20unwilling%20to%20return%20to%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20equally%20important%20area%20to%20consider%20is%20the%20loss%20of%20faith%20and%20trust%20in%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%2C%20including%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20policemen.%20The%20Kuki%20MLAs%20believe%20that%20the%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20failed%20miserably%20in%20safeguarding%20lives%20and%20maintaining%20law%20and%20order%2C%20alleging%20collusion%20with%20the%20violent%20Meitei%20mobs.%20There%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Ereports%20that%20suggest%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20state%20police%20cooperated%20with%20the%20Meitei%20mobs%20when%20Kuki%20civilians%20and%20villages%20were%20being%20attacked.%20This%20could%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20accounts%20of%20the%20rape%20victims%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20policemen%20%E2%80%93%20who%20were%20on%20duty%20%E2%80%93%20were%20present%20during%20the%20crime%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-the-indian-state-has-gone-into-hiding-in-manipur-says-harsh-mander%5C%22%3Edidn%E2%80%99t%20help%20them.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20countless%20atrocities%20and%20abuses%20that%20happened%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Imphal%20city%20fail%20to%20get%20due%20attention%20or%20attract%20%3Cem%3Esuo%20moto%20cognizance%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Eparticularly%20when%20the%20victim%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20is%20the%20credibility%20the%20state%20police%20have%20earned%20over%20the%20past%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-violence-claims-counterclaims-meitei-kuki%5C%22%3EDispelling%20Some%20Misleading%20Claims%20About%20the%20Violence%20in%20Manipur%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20violence%20reshaped%20the%20principles%20of%20coexistence%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kuki%20MLAs%20have%20called%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20with%20an%20independent%20DGP%20who%20can%20ensure%20fairness%2C%20protect%20lives%2C%20and%20maintain%20law%20and%20order%20without%20bias%20toward%20any%20community.%20This%20demand%20arises%20from%20the%20compelling%20need%20to%20secure%20the%20welfare%20and%20safety%20of%20the%20Kuki%20people%2C%20who%20have%20endured%20discrimination%20and%20hate%20for%20seven%20decades.%20Now%2C%20the%20violence%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community%20against%20the%20Kukis%20has%20accelerated%20the%20call%20for%20separation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20elites%20among%20the%20Kuki%20community%20%E2%80%93%20who%20are%20largely%20lukewarm%20to%20any%20political%20settlement%20%E2%80%93%20became%20the%20first%20casualty%20of%20the%20violence.%20They%20had%20wielded%20strong%20control%20over%20Kuki%20political%20movements%20for%20the%20past%20many%20years.%20They%20believe%20in%20peaceful%20coexistence%20and%20are%20therefore%20opposed%20to%20Naga%20integration%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20past%20three%20months%20have%20completely%20reshaped%20the%20principles%20of%20coexistence%20like%20never%20before.%20In%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-manipur-cm-anti-kuki-separate-state-wilson-lalam-hangshing-karan-thapar%5C%22%3Einterview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20hosted%20by%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20Kuki%20People%20Alliance%20(KPA)%2C%20W.L.%20Hangshing%20noted%20that%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20divided%20the%20people%20from%20the%20Kuki%20and%20Meitei%20communities%2C%20physically%20and%20emotionally.%20He%20further%20pointed%20out%20that%20as%20separation%20has%20already%20been%20completed%2C%20it%20is%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20recognise%20and%20give%20them%20powers%20to%20govern%20themselves%20as%20two%20separate%20political%20entities%20to%20avoid%20further%20conflicts%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifp.co.in%2Fmanipur%2Fupf-kno-hold-talks-with-goi-put-up-demand-for-ut-with-legislative-powers%5C%22%3Eaccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnortheastlivetv.com%2Ftopnews%2Fmanipur-upf-and-kno-to-resume-formal-talks-with-centre-on-july-26%2F%5C%22%3Eto%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatodayne.in%2Fmanipur%2Fstory%2Fmanipur-violence-union-territory-with-legislative-powers-put-up-during-talks-between-kuki-insurgent-groups-and-centre-623147-2023-07-28%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20Kuki%20insurgent%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20UPF%20and%20KNO%20%E2%80%93%20are%20in%20the%20final%20rounds%20of%20negotiation%20with%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20A%20separate%20political%20entity%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20Union%20territory%20with%20legislative%20powers%2C%20a%20Territorial%20Council%20or%20a%20Special%20Autonomy%20under%20specific%20provisions%20of%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20are%20the%20demands%20put%20forth%20by%20the%20militant%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhatever%20it%20is%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20in%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20court.%20It%E2%80%99s%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20serious%20it%20is%20in%20solving%20the%20insurgency%20in%20Manipur%20and%20the%20North%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20not%20serious%20enough%20in%20considering%20the%20Kuki%20people%E2%80%99s%20problem%2C%20because%20it%20is%20opposed%20by%20a%20certain%20community%2C%20then%20it%20could%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20failure%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20system.%20It%20will%20set%20a%20negative%20precedent%20for%20all%20decision-making%20matters%20vested%20in%20the%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20it%20must%20be%20prepared%20for%20a%20new%20wave%20of%20insurgency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kukis%E2%80%99%20loyalty%20to%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20the%20constitution%20should%20not%20be%20tested%20anymore.%20They%20fought%20the%20British%20for%20almost%20three%20years%20and%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fhow-manipurs-kukis-meiteis-and-nagas-were-united-to-the-inas-cause-to-free-india%5C%22%3Ejoined%20hands%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%E2%80%99s%20Indian%20National%20Army%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle.%20Of%20the%20total%20193%20freedom%20fighters%20of%20Manipur%20listed%20in%20the%20INA%20Museum%20at%20Moirang%20in%20Manipur%2C%20159%20belonged%20to%20the%20Kuki%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Cem%3EBande%20Mataram%3A%20Freedom%20Fighters%20of%20Manipur%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheshillongtimes.com%2F2023%2F06%2F13%2Fnarratives-of-hate-behind-manipur-violence%2F%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Congress%20party%20in%201986%2C%2079%20out%20of%20the%20total%20of%20112%20are%20Kukis.%20No%20other%20community%20in%20Manipur%20can%20match%20their%20contribution%20towards%20India%E2%80%99s%20freedom%20struggle.%20However%2C%20they%20were%20denied%20the%20rightful%20place%20by%20successive%20governments%20for%20the%20past%20seven%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20the%20Kukis%20strongly%20believed%20in%20the%20Union%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20call%20for%20a%20separate%20entity%20in%20Manipur%20is%20primarily%20driven%20by%20the%20Kukis%E2%80%99%20urgent%20need%20to%20safeguard%20their%20welfare%20and%20security%20in%20response%20to%20a%20significant%20existential%20threat.%20Unlike%20the%20demands%20of%20neighbouring%20communities%20like%20the%20Meiteis%20and%20the%20Nagas%2C%20this%20aspiration%20does%20not%20pose%20a%20challenge%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20India.%20The%20current%20demand%20might%20not%20have%20arisen%20if%20not%20for%20the%20substantial%20threats%20posed%20by%20the%20Meitei%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20dealings%20with%20the%20Manipur%20government%2C%20the%20Kukis%20seem%20to%20have%20reached%20a%20point%20of%20no%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20writer%20teaches%20journalism%20at%20Royal%20Global%20University%2C%20Guwahati.%20He%20can%20be%20contacted%20at%3A%20lienchongloi%