said%20that%20he%20was%20first%20intrigued%20by%20biofuels%20way%20back%20in%202004%20when%20petrol%20prices%20started%20spiking.%20He%20visited%20Brazil%20to%20understand%20how%20a%20shift%20to%20biofuels%20could%20change%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Biofuel%20Shift%20Means%20For%20India%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIndia%20depends%20on%20oil%20imports%20to%20meet%20fuel%20needs%2C%20causing%20great%20stress%20on%20the%20state%20coffers.%20According%20to%20Mr%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-nitin-gadkari-introduces-marvel-of-engineering-dwarka-expressway-4314405%5C%22%3EGadkari%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20current%20import%20bill%20for%20petroleum%20is%20around%20Rs%2016%20lakh%20crore.%20With%20a%20shift%20to%20biofuel%20options%20such%20as%20ethanol%2C%20derived%20from%20plant-based%20sources%20like%20sugarcane%2C%20the%20oil%20import%20bills%20could%20be%20cut%20down%2C%20making%20the%20country%20more%20self-reliant%20to%20meet%20its%20fuel%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20want%20to%20become%20%3Cem%3Eatmanirbhar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(self-reliant)%20we%20have%20to%20bring%20this%20oil%20import%20to%20zero.%20At%20present%2C%20it%20is%20%E2%82%B916%20lakh%20crore.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20loss%20to%20the%20economy.%20India%20needs%20to%20take%20more%20sustainable%20measures%20as%20pollution%20is%20a%20big%20problem%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gadkari%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20Mint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Does%20It%20Change%20the%20Game%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20use%20of%20biofuels%20will%20also%20help%20in%20curbing%20pollution.%20To%20push%20bio-fuel%20consumption%2C%20India%2C%20last%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Fpetrol-mixed-with-20-ethanol-starts-rolled-out-for-sale-in-11-states-3756938%5C%22%3Erolled%20out%20petrol%20mixed%20with%2020%20per%20cent%20ethanol%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20plan%20is%20to%20double%20the%20quantity%20of%20ethanol%20by%202025.%20The%20use%20of%2020%20per%20cent%20ethanol-blended%20petrol%20is%20estimated%20to%20cut%20carbon%20monoxide%20emission%20by%2050%20per%20cent%20in%20two-wheelers%20and%20about%2030%20per%20cent%20in%20four-wheelers%20compared%20to%20neat%20petrol.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693293720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Fulb92mh8_toyota-innova-hycross_650x400_18_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-benefits-of-a-car-running-100-on-ethanol-explained-4338266%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20for%20Road%20Transport%20and%20Highway%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20is%20set%20to%20unveil%20a%20100%20per%20cent%20ethanol%20fuel%20variant%20of%20Toyota%20Innova%20MPV%20on%20Tuesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-benefits-of-a-car-running-100-on-ethanol-explained-4338266%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-benefits-of-a-car-running-100-on-ethanol-explained-4338266%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthe-benefits-of-a-car-running-100-on-ethanol-explained-4338266%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26amp%3BK%3A%20IAS%20Officer%20From%20Dalit%20Community%20Accuses%20LG%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%20of%20%E2%80%98Harassment%2C%20Humiliation'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2F26190346%2FScreen-Shot-2021-04-26-at-7.03.28-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Ashok%20Kumar%20Parmar%2C%20an%20IAS%20officer%20who%20is%20from%20the%20Dalit%20community%2C%20has%20accused%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Lt%20Governor%20(LG)%20Manoj%20Sinha%20and%20chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Mehta%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinflicting%20harassment%20and%20humiliation%20upon%20him%E2%80%9D%20because%20he%20highlighted%20%E2%80%9Cbunglings%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20complaint%20to%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(NCSC)%2C%20Parmar%20%E2%80%93%20a%201992%20AGMUT%20cadre%20officer%20%E2%80%93%20accuses%20Sinha%20and%20Mehta%20of%20%E2%80%9Charassment%2C%20humiliation%2C%20intimidation%2C%20atrocious%20behaviour%20and%20frequent%20transfers%20for%20his%20being%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20solely%20for%20the%20reason%20that%20he%20blew%20%5Bthe%5D%20whistle%20and%20highlighted%20bunglings%20in%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20plans%20to%20provide%20every%20rural%20household%20with%20tap%20water%20by%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20is%20currently%20posted%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Public%20Enterprises%20and%20was%20principal%20secretary%20of%20the%20Jal%20Shakti%20Department%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20in%20May%202022%2C%20during%20which%20time%20he%20said%20he%20intimated%20the%20LG%2C%20chief%20secretary%20and%20other%20authorities%20about%20the%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cdismal%20status%20of%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20being%20implemented%20without%20doing%20SWOT%20(Strengths%2C%20Weaknesses%2C%20Opportunities%20and%20Threats)%20Analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20JJM%20works%20were%20progressing%20slowly%20%E2%80%9Cbecause%20of%20erroneous%20and%20faulty%20procedure%20for%20allotment%20of%20works%E2%80%9D%20and%20misinterpretation%20of%20a%20clause%20of%20the%20Manual%20of%20Procurement%20of%20Works%2C%202019%20that%20one%20contractor%20can%20be%20awarded%20only%20two%20works%20at%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestatesman.com%2Findia%2Fjk-dalit-ias-officer-files-complaint-of-harassment-humiliation-against-l-g-chief-secretary-1503216550.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Statesman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Parmar%20claims%20that%20LG%20Sinha%20on%20June%206%2C%202022%20threw%20him%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20room%20with%20the%20objective%20to%20%E2%80%9Charass%20and%20humiliate%20him%20without%20any%20fault%20and%20this%20was%20done%20in%20front%20of%20all%20the%20administrative%20secretaries%20of%20UT%20of%20J%26amp%3BK.%E2%80%9D%20Chief%20secretary%20Arun%20Kumar%20Mehta%20on%20July%2025%2C%202023%20also%20%E2%80%9Chumiliated%20and%20threw%20him%20out%20of%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20Committee%20of%20Secretaries%20without%20any%20fault%E2%80%9D.%20Parmar%20said%20he%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20%E2%80%9Cfrequent%20transfers%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20transfer%20policy%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20to%20the%20NCSC%20says%20that%20this%20process%20of%20%E2%80%9Cintimidation%20and%20harassment%20was%20done%20purposely%20due%20to%20prejudice%20and%20bias%20against%20him%20for%20being%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20and%20his%20act%20of%20highlighting%20bunglings%20in%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IAS%20officer%20said%20he%20has%20apprehensions%20that%20LG%20Sinha%20chief%20secretary%20Mehta%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20go%20to%20any%20extent%20to%20damage%20his%20reputation%20and%20career%20by%20implicating%20him%20in%20false%20cases%20as%20he%20had%20pointed%20out%20many%20financial%20irregularities%20and%20acts%20of%20omission%20and%20commission%20of%20Mehta%2C%20Chief%20Secretary%2C%20RR%20Bhatnagar%20Advisor%20to%20LG%20and%20others%20in%20the%20implementation%20of%20Jal%20Jeevan%20Mission%E2%80%9D%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Statesman%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParmar%20said%20he%20has%20also%20informed%20the%C2%A0Prime%20Minister%