'%20Places%20In%20Arunachal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20the%20Indian%20government%20rejected%20China's%20bid%20to%20rename%2011%20locations%20within%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20it%20also%20calls%20'Zangnan'%20-%20the%20third%20time%20Beijing%20has%20attempted%20such%20an%20egregious%20move%20after%202018%20and%202021%20-%20and%20asserted%20the%20northeastern%20state%20has%20been%20and%20will%20always%20be%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Findia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndia%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-releases-new-names-for-11-places-in-latest-arunachal-push-3918324%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BInvented%20Names%26quot%3B%3A%20India%20Rejects%20China%20'Renaming'%20Places%20In%20Arunachal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20places%20'renamed'%20included%20five%20mountain%20peaks%2C%20two%20residential%20areas%20and%20two%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20seen%20such%20reports.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20China%20has%20made%20such%20an%20attempt.%20We%20reject%20this%20outright%2C%26quot%3B%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BArunachal%20Pradesh%20is%2C%20has%20been%2C%20and%20will%20always%20be%20an%20integral%20and%20inalienable%20part%20of%20India.%20Attempts%20to%20assign%20invented%20names%20will%20not%20alter%20this%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EIndia-China%20Clashes%20in%20Arunachal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20clashed%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20state's%20Tawang%20sector%20in%20December%20last%20year%20-%20a%20face-off%20that%20came%20amid%20a%20months-long%20border%20standoff%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20that%20prompted%20Delhi%20to%20bolster%20overall%20military%20readiness%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20sector%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp