%20with%20a%20cot%20mattress%2C%20four%20pillows%2C%20a%20table%2C%20a%20chair%2C%20a%20prayer%20mat%20and%20an%20air%20cooler.%20Likewise%2C%20the%20report%20stated%20that%20reading%20material%2C%20including%20four%20copies%20of%20the%20Holy%20Quran%20with%20an%20English%20translation%20and%2025%20numbers%20of%20books%20of%20Islamic%20history%20had%20also%20been%20provided%20to%20the%20convicted%20prisoner%20besides%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20district%20and%20sessions%20court%20on%20August%205%2C%20sentenced%20Imran%20Khan%20to%20three%20years%20in%20prison%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20case%20i.e.%20for%20illegally%20selling%20state%20gifts%20and%20disqualified%20him%20from%20politics%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20years%2C%20local%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20Chairman%20was%20arrested%20from%20his%20Zaman%20Park%20residence%20in%20Lahore%20soon%20after%20being%20convicted%20in%20the%20Toshakhana%20case.%20The%20court%20also%20imposed%20a%20fine%20of%20Pakistani%20Rupees%20(PKR)%20100%2C000%20on%20Imran%20Khan%2C%20Geo%20News%20reported.%20Khan%2C%20who%20has%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20over%20being%20in%20jail%20and%20said%20that%20he%20doesn't%20want%20to%20stay%20there%2C%20Pakistan-based%20Geo%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PTI%20Chairman%20Imran%20Khan%20had%20also%20stated%20that%20he%20remains%20holed%20up%20inside%20his%20prison%20cell%20in%20%26quot%3Bdistressing%26quot%3B%20conditions%2C%20as%20per%20the%20sources.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693291320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhkla3vog_imran-khanpakistan_625x300_19_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fimran-khan-served-desi-chicken-mutton-in-jail-pakistan-attorney-gen