avel%2Fnews-and-advice%2Fkorean-air-weight-limit-passengers-b2400433.html%5C%22%3EIndependent%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3Ereported.%C2%A0Korean%20Air%20confirmed%20on%20its%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreanair.com%2Fil%2Fen%2Ffooter%2Fcustomer-support%2Fnotice%2F2023%2F2308-weight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20it%20would%20be%20''measuring%20the%20average%20weight%20of%20passengers%20along%20with%20their%20carry-on%20items%20for%20flight%20safety''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20is%20used%20to%20help%20determine%20the%20weight%20distribution%20of%20aircraft%2C%20and%20calculations%20need%20to%20take%20place%20every%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weighing%20will%20take%20place%20in%20front%20of%20the%20gates%20and%20before%20boarding%2C%3Cem%3E%20The%20Korea%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20initiative%20has%20already%20been%20rolled%20out%20for%20domestic%20passengers%20at%20Gimpo%20International%20Airport%20from%20August%2028%20to%20September%206%2C%20followed%20by%20international%20passengers%20at%20Incheon%20International%20Airport%20from%20September%208%20to%20September%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fcllonaolt000k3b6igwoifgii%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EFor%20any%C2%A0passengers%20who%20are%20uncomfortable%20about%20the%20process%2C%20the%20airlines%20said%20that%20both%20passengers%20and%20luggage%20will%20be%20weighed%20anonymously.%C2%A0If%20a%20passenger%20is%20still%20skeptical%20and%20chooses%20not%20to%20participate%20in%20these%20weight%20measurements%2C%C2%A0they%20can%20opt-out%20by%20letting%20a%20staff%20member%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20all%20the%20data%20is%20collected%20it%20will%20be%20shared%20with%20Korea's%20Ministry%20of%20Land%2C%20Infrastructure%20and%20Transport%20and%20will%20help%20the%20airlines%20determine%20how%20much%20fuel%20is%20needed%20and%20how%20to%20distribute%20weight%20onboard%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20data%20collated%20anonymously%20will%20be%20utilized%20for%20survey%20purposes%20and%20doesn't%20mean%20overweight%20passengers%20will%20need%20to%20pay%20more%2C''%20the%20airline%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20this%20year%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fthis-airline-will-weigh-passengers-before-they-board-flights-4079328%5C%22%3E%20Air%20New%20Zealand%20started%20weighing%20passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%20departing%20on%20international%20flights%20from%20the%20Auckland%20International%20Airport.%20The%20flag%20carrier%20said%20the%20program%2C%20which%20the%20airline%20called%20a%20passenger%20weight%20survey%2C%20is%20a%20way%20to%20gather%20data%20on%20the%20weight%20load%20and%20distribution%20of%20planes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDescribed%20as%20an%20'essential'%20initiative%2C%20the%20survey%20is%20being%20used%20to%20determine%20the%20average%20customer%20weight%2C%20which%20pilots%20need%20to%20know%20before%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693288620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fvvd2iph8_korean-air_625x300_29_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-air-new-zealand-another-airline-to-weigh-passengers-before-boarding-plane-4338329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20process%20is%20used%20to%20help%20determine%20the%20weight%20distribution%20of%20aircraft%2C%20and%20calculations%20need%20to%20take%20place%20every%20five%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fafter-air-new-zealand-another-airline-to-weigh-passengers-before-boarding-plane-4338329%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2F