ttps%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgeetika-srivastava-is-first-woman-to-head-indian-mission-in-pakistan-8913817%2F%5C%22%3Edowngraded%20its%20status%20of%20diplomatic%20representation%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20withdrawal%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20special%20status%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20Islamabad%20was%20Ajay%20Bisaria%2C%20who%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgeetika-srivastava-is-first-woman-to-head-indian-mission-in-pakistan-8913817%2F%5C%22%3Ewithdrawn%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20move%20and%20the%20high%20commissions%20in%20both%20countries%20have%20since%20been%20headed%20by%20a%20CDA%20who%20is%20a%20joint%20secretary-rank%20equivalent%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20will%20also%20be%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20head%20the%20Indian%20mission%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgeetika-srivastava-is-first-woman-to-head-indian-mission-in-pakistan-8913817%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%201947%2C%20when%20Sri%20Prakasa%20was%20sent%20as%20the%20Indian%20high%20commissioner%20to%20the%20then%20Dominion%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20New%20Delhi%20has%20always%20been%20represented%20by%20male%20diplomats%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20There%20have%20been%2022%20heads%20of%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrivastava%2C%20who%20learned%20Mandarin%20as%20part%20of%20her%20foreign%20language%20training%2C%20has%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20China%20during%202007-09%2C%20had%20stints%20at%20the%20Regional%20Passport%20Office%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20as%20director%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20division%20in%20the%20MEA.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693287875000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29105701%2FFfsXzaqUUAAY81--e1693287828600.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgeetika-srivastava-to-head-indian-mission-in-pakistan-first-woman-after-22-male-representatives%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22She%20will%20be%20the%20senior%20most%20Indian%20diplomat%20in%20Islamabad%20as%20Pakistan%20and%20India%20no%20longer%20have%20high%20commissioners%20in%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20capital%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fgeetika-srivastava-to-head-indian-mission-in-pakistan-first-woman-after-22-male-representatives%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Provokes%20India%2C%20Includes%20Arunachal%2C%20Aksai%20Chin%20In%20New%20%26quot%3BStandard%20Map%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20officially%20released%20the%202023%20edition%20of%20its%20%E2%80%9Cstandard%20map%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20shows%20the%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20region%20as%20part%20of%20its%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20released%20on%20August%2028%20shows%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20which%20China%20claims%20as%20South%20Tibet%20and%20Aksai%20Chin%20occupied%20by%20it%20in%20the%201962%20war%20as%20part%20of%20its%20territory.%20Taiwan%20and%20the%20disputed%20South%20China%20Sea%20are%20also%20included%20within%20the%20Chinese%20territory%20in%20the%20new%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20also%20incorporates%20China's%20claims%20over%20the%20nine-dash%20line%20thus%20laying%20claim%20to%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20South%20China%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVietnam%2C%20the%C2%A0Philippines%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20and%20Brunei%20have%20all%20claims%20over%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20map%20was%20released%20by%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Natural%20Resources%20during%20the%20celebration%20of%20Surveying%20and%20Mapping%20Publicity%20Day%20and%20the%20National%20Mapping%20Awareness%20Publicity%20Week%20on%20Monday%20in%20Deqing%20county%2C%20Zhejiang%20province%2C%20as%20per%20China%20Daily%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Xi%20Jinping%20met%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20BRICS%20Summit%20in%20Johannesburg%2C%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Secretary%20Vinay%20Kwatra%20had%20said%20in%20his%20conversation%20with%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20highlighted%20India's%20concerns%20on%20unresolved%20issues%20along%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20in%20the%20Western%20Sector%20of%20the%20India-China%20border%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Prime%20Minister%20underlined%20that%20maintenance%20of%20peace%20and%20tranquillity%20in%20the%20border%20areas%20and%20observing%20and%20respecting%20the%20LAC%20are%20essential%20for%20the%20normalisation%20of%20the%C2%A0India-China%C2%A0relationship.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20two%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20direct%20their%20relevant%20officials%20to%20intensify%20efforts%20at%20expeditious%20disengagement%20and%20de-escalation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kwatra%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20planner%20of%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Natural%20Resources%2C%20Wu%20Wenzhong%2C%20said%20surveying%2C%20mapping%20and%20geographic%20information%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20boosting%20the%20development%20of%20the%20nation%2C%20meeting%20the%20needs%20of%20all%20walks%20of%20life%2C%20supporting%20the%20management%20of%20natural%20resources%2C%20and%20helping%20the%20construction%20of%20ecology%20and%20civilization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20next%20step%20will%20be%20to%20accelerate%20the%20application%20of%20geographic%20information%20data%20such%20as%20digital%20maps%20and%20navigation%20and%20positioning%20in%20the%20development%20of%20the%20digital%20economy%2C%20such%20as%20location-based%20services%2C%20precision%20agriculture%2C%20platform%20economy%20and%20intelligent%20connected%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Wu%20said%2C%20as%20per%20China%20Daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZhejiang%20has%20in%20recent%20years%20focused%20on%20the%20deep%20integration%20of%20the%20digital%20and%20real%20economies%20and%20has%20continued%20to%20promote%20the%20development%20of%20the%20digital%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20Li%20Yaowu%2C%20deputy%20secretary-general%20of%20the%20Zhejiang%20Provincial%20People's%20Government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20territorial%20disputes%20with%20more%20countries%20than%20it%20shares%20its%20borders%20with.%20The%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%2C%20the%20CCP%2C%20with%20Xi%20Jinping%20at%20the%20helm%2C%20has%20used%20deceitful%20tactics%20and%20manipulation%20in%20order%20to%20attempt%20to%20assert%20territorial%20control%20over%20other%20sovereign%20territories.%20Beijing%20has%20flouted%20all%20international%20norms%20in%20its%20expansionist%20bid%20to%20control%20more%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%C2%A0has%20now%20staked%20claims%20on%20parts%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20arguing%20that%20these%20locations%20were%20part%20of%20greater%20Tibet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20desperate%20Beijing%20had%20in%20April%20this%20year%20unilaterally%20%E2%80%9Crenamed%E2%80%9D%20as%20many%20as%2011%C2%A0Indian%20locations%2C%20which%20included%20names%20of%20mountain%20peaks%2C%20rivers%20and%20residential%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20Beijing%20has%20employed%20such%20tactics.%20Previously%20in%202017%20and%202021%2C%C2%A0China's%20Civil%20Affair%20Ministry%20had%20renamed%20other%C2%A0Indian%20locations%20triggering%20another%20political%20confrontation.%20New%20Delhi%20called%20out%C2%A0China's%20expansionist%20plans%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20the%20official%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20Arindam%20Bagchi%2C%20while%20commenting%20on%20China's%20attempt%20to%20show%20its%20domination%20in%20places%20belonging%20to%20India's%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20China%20has%20attempted%20something%20like%20this%20(changing%20the%20names%20of%20areas%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh)%20and%20we%20have%20already%20condemned%20any%20such%20attempts.%20Regarding%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20we%20had%20also%20said%20that%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20is%20an%20inseparable%20part%20of%20India)%20and%20imposing%20invented%20names%20like%20these%20will%20not%20at%20all%20change%20the%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693287840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-06%2F9jubsjh_arunachal-pradeshgenericunsplash_625x300_11_June_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-provokes-india-includes-arunachal-pradesh-in-new-standard-map-4338224%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20officially%20released%20the%202023%20edition%20of%20its%20%26quot%3Bstandard%20map%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20shows%20the%20state%20of%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Aksai%20Chin%20region%20as%20part%20of%20its%20territory.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-provokes-india-includes-arunachal-pradesh-in-new-standard-map-4338224%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-provokes-india-includes-arunachal-pradesh-in-new-standard-map-4338224%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchina-provokes-india-includes-arunachal-pradesh-in-new-standard-map-4338224%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aamir%20sings%20at%20Laal%20Singh%20Chaddha%20reunion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2