20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20president%20Sharad%20Pawar%20appears%20to%20have%20indicated%20that%20a%20return%20by%20his%20nephew%20into%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20fold%20is%20unlikely.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20his%20daughter%20and%20NCP%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20party%2C%20the%20NCP%20chief%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20assert%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20our%20leader.%20It%20was%20Supriya%20Sule%20who%20made%20that%20statement.%20Their%20relationship%20is%20akin%20to%20siblings%2C%20devoid%20of%20any%20political%20connotation.%20My%20statement%20didn%E2%80%99t%20designate%20Ajit%20Pawar%20as%20our%20leader.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20statement%20triggered%20varied%20interpretations%20within%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20opposition%20and%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20insinuated%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20allegiance%20was%20veering%20towards%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20The%20opposition%20camp%20contended%20that%20the%20elder%20Pawar%20was%20deftly%20bewildering%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENana%20Patole%2C%20the%20head%20of%20Maharashtra%20Congress%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20his%20uncle%20might%20have%20led%20to%20a%20desire%20for%20return.%20%E2%80%9CSharad%20Pawar%20appears%20to%20have%20succeeded%20in%20changing%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20mind.%20There%20is%20no%20confusion%20in%20Congress%20and%20the%20Uddhav-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20about%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20We%20firmly%20stand%20behind%20Sharad%20Pawar.%20It%20is%20for%20them%20to%20decide%20what%20is%20going%20on%20in%20the%20NCP%20and%20what%20steps%20they%20should%20take%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nana%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Chandrashekhar%20Bawankule%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20chief%2C%20told%20local%20media%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20a%20votary%20of%20developmental%20politics%2C%20was%20on%20the%20cusp%20of%20aligning%20with%20the%20NDA.%20By%20claiming%20Pawar%20as%20an%20ally%2C%20Bawankule%20proclaimed%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20supremacy%20in%20the%20forthcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharashtra-ajit-sharad-pawar-ncp%5C%22%3EMaharashtra%3A%20Is%20the%20Stage%20Being%20Set%20for%20Ajit%20to%20Reunite%20With%20Sharad%20Pawar%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Opportunity%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20talking%20to%20the%20press%20in%20Kolhapur%20on%20August%2025%2C%20Pawar%20cleared%20the%20air%20about%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20presumed%20return%20to%20his%20original%20party.%20He%20said%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cchance%E2%80%9D%20was%20given%20to%20him%20to%20make%20a%20return%20after%202019%2C%20when%20Ajit%20had%20allied%20with%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20to%20form%20the%20Maharashtra%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20may%20recall%20a%20particular%20incident%20when%20an%20early%20morning%20oath%20ceremony%20took%20place%20between%20two%20individuals.%20One%20of%20our%20colleagues%20was%20involved%20in%20this%20event.%20At%20that%20juncture%2C%20we%20made%20a%20resolve.%20Despite%20vowing%20not%20to%20tread%20that%20path%20again%2C%20we%20opted%20for%20a%20different%20course%20of%20action%2C%20viewing%20it%20as%20an%20opportunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarked%20Sharad%20Pawar%20in%20Kolhapur.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20same%20opportunity%20cannot%20be%20given%20to%20him%20again%20and%20again%20and%20it%20should%20not%20be%20sought%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Pawar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20Sharad%20Pawar%20claiming%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20in%20the%20party%2C%20maximum%20MLAs%20of%20the%20NCP%20appear%20to%20be%20with%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction.%20Nine%20minsters%20in%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20come%20from%20the%20NCP%2C%20but%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20consistently%20said%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20in%20the%20party.%20Even%20Supriya%20Sule%20reiterated%20this%20claim%20by%20enforcing%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20in%20the%20NCP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20such%20a%20stance%3F%20It%20is%20speculated%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20refusing%20to%20acknowledge%20this%20split%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20stop%20the%20Election%20Commission%20from%20handing%20over%20the%20party%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20ECI%20recognised%20Eknath%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20faction%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Creal%E2%80%9D%20Shiv%20Sena%20based%20on%20the%20number%20of%20MLAs%20each%20faction%20had.%20The%20poll%20body%20also%20announced%20that%20Shinde%E2%80%99s%20team%20will%20get%20the%20%E2%80%98bow-and-arrow%E2%80%99%20symbol%2C%20the%20original%20party%20symbol.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESharad%20Pawar%20appears%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20such%20an%20outcome%20and%20thus%2C%20since%20the%20day%20Ajit%20joined%20ranks%20with%20BJP%20along%20with%20eight%20other%20MLAs%20who%20took%20oath%20as%20minister%2C%20the%20elder%20Pawar%20has%20maintained%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20in%20the%20NCP.%20In%20fact%2C%20NCP%20has%20initiated%20disqualification%20proceedings%20against%20only%20nine%20of%20its%20MLAs%2C%20those%20who%20took%20oath%20as%20minsters%20in%20the%20Shinde%20government.%20Earlier%20in%20August%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20told%20the%20Election%20Commission%20that%20there%20is%20no%20split%20and%20NCP%20remains%20united.%20We%20are%20the%20real%20party%20and%20no%20one%20can%20stake%20a%20claim%20on%20it%E2%80%A6%20The%20Election%20Commission%20should%20not%20have%20taken%20cognisance%20of%20their%20letter%20because%20no%20such%20split%20has%20ever%20happened%20and%20the%20party%20stands%20united.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20sent%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20a%20petition%20under%20Para%2015%20of%20Election%20Symbols%20Order%20to%20recognise%20him%20as%20the%20president%20of%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20same%20was%20repeated%20by%20Jitendra%20Awhad%2C%20a%20Sharad%20Pawar%20loyalist.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20press%20conference%20on%20Friday%20where%20he%20refused%20to%20see%20Ajit%20Pawar%20as%20a%20NCP%20leader%2C%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav%2C%20a%20five-time%20MLA%20from%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20said%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20is%20cautious%20so%20that%20%E2%80%9Cnone%20of%20his%20statements%20lead%20to%20unintended%20complications%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDescribing%20Sharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20approach%20as%20equivalent%20to%20locating%20a%20needle%20in%20the%20haystack%2C%20Jadhav%20said%20to%20the%20channel%20%E2%80%98ABP%20Maja%E2%80%99%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CSharad%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20statements%20often%20invite%20a%20myriad%20of%20interpretations%2C%20leading%20many%20to%20delve%20into%20the%20details%20of%20his%20position.%20The%20enigmatic%20nature%20of%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20stance%20has%20left%20some%20perplexed%2C%20and%20some%20have%20even%20lost%20their%20way%20trying%20to%20unravel%20its%20rationale.%20Pawar%20is%20in%20a%20battle%20against%20the%20MLAs%20who%20defected%20from%20the%20NCP%2C%20additionally%2C%20he%20remains%20entangled%20in%20a%20political%20as%20well%20as%20a%20legal%20battle.%20Jayant%20Patil%20has%20formally%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20against%209%20MLAs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20Sharad%20Pawar%20cautiously%20navigates%20to%20ensure%20that%20none%20of%20his%20statements%20lead%20to%20unintended%20complications.%20We%20all%20saw%20what%20happened%20with%20Shiv%20Sena.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Ajit%20Pawar%20does%20not%20want%20to%20be%20disqualified%2C%20he%20can%20come%20back.%20Because%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%20has%20not%20left%20any%20other%20door%20open%20for%20Ajit%20Pawar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693287733000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F06084439%2FUntitled-design-3.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharad-pawar-ajit-election-commission-ncp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20speculated%20that%20Sharad%20Pawar%20refusing%20to%20acknowledge%20this%20split%20is%20a%20ploy%20to%20stop%20the%20Election%20Commission%20from%20handing%20over%20the%20party%20to%20Ajit%20Pawar.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsharad-pawar-ajit-election-commission-ncp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2212%20Companies%20Benefitted%20From%20Short%20Selling%20In%20Adani%20Group%20Shares%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20dozen%20companies%2C%20including%20foreign%20portfolio%20investors%20and%20foreign%20institutional%20investors%20in%20tax%20havens%2C%20were%20the%20top%20beneficiaries%20from%20short%20selling%20in%20shares%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fhindenburg-report-probe-short-selling-in-adani-shares-led-to-gains-for-12-firms-ed-to-sebi-8913806%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%20citing%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20probe%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20that%20led%20to%20a%20market%20crash%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShort-selling%20refers%20to%20the%20investing%20technique%20where%20securities%20are%20borrowed%20to%20sell%20and%20later%20bought%20back%20when%20the%20price%20dips.%20In%20this%20model%2C%20investors%20bet%20on%20and%20make%20profits%20from%20a%20fall%20in%20share%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20had%20shared%20its%20findings%20with%20markets%20regulator%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)%20in%20July%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20the%20short%20sellers%2C%20which%20included%20three%20from%20India%20and%20four%20from%20Mauritius%2C%20had%20disclosed%20their%20ownership%20structures%20to%20income%20tax%20authorities%2C%20the%20report%20cited%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20companies%20had%20allegedly%20opened%20positions%20two%20to%20three%20days%20before%20the%20Hindenburg%20report%20was%20published%20on%20January%2024%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20Some%20others%20were%20dabbling%20in%20short%20trades%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20investors%20that%20registered%20with%20SEBI%20are%20allowed%20to%20trade%20in%20derivatives%2C%20the%20financial%20instruments%20that%20allow%20short-term%20trades%20by%20offsetting%20market%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20pointed%20to%20irregular%20earning%20patterns%20of%20some%20of%20these%20short%20sellers.%20The%20SEBI%20had%20passed%20an%20order%20against%20the%20promoter%20of%20one%20of%20the%20Indian%20firms%20for%20misleading%20investors%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20had%20alleged%20that%20industrialist%20Gautam%20Adani%20used%20shell%20companies%20in%20Mauritius%20to%20manipulate%20stock%20prices%20of%20Adani%20Group%20firms.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20has%20denied%20all%20charges%20and%20called%20its%20report%20a%20%26quot%3Bcalculated%20attack%26quot%3B%20on%20India%2C%20its%20institutions%20and%20growth%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20SEBI%20to%20investigate%20the%20case%20and%20submit%20a%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20panel%20of%20experts%20appointed%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20earlier%20submitted%20there%20was%20no%20price%20manipulation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20Adani%20Group%20and%20that%20the%20conglomerate%20had%20taken%20necessary%20steps%20to%20comfort%20retail%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693287540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fuvocqub_ed-generic-enforcement-directorate-generic_625x300_20_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-short-sellers-benefitted-from-short-selling-in-adani-group-shares-report-4338309%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20dozen%20companies%20were%20the%20top%20beneficiaries%20from%20short%20selling%20in%20shares%20of%20Adani%20Group%20companies%2C%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20found%20during%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20Hindenburg%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-short-sellers-benefitted-from-short-selling-in-adani-group-shares-report-4338309%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-short-sellers-benefitted-from-short-selling-in-adani-group-shares-report-4338309%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F12-short-sellers-benefitted-from-short-selling-in-adani-group-shares-report-4338309%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Toyota%20halts%20all%20Japan%20assembly%20plants%20due%20to%20glitch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693287318000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0AB6%2Fproduction%2F_1309