udents%20of%20a%20Delhi%20school%20have%20alleged%20that%20their%20teacher%20made%20communal%20remarks%20and%20asked%20them%20why%20their%20families%20did%20not%20go%20to%20Pakistan%20during%20Partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20amid%20the%20outrage%20over%20a%20viral%20video%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Muzaffarnagar%2C%20where%20students%20are%20seen%20slapping%20a%20Muslim%20classmate%20on%20the%20order%20of%20their%20teacher.%20The%20teacher%2C%20Tripta%20Tyagi%2C%20is%20heard%20making%20communal%20remarks%20in%20the%20video%20from%20Muzaffarnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20have%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20Hema%20Gulati%2C%20a%20teacher%20at%20Government%20Sarvodaya%20Bal%20Vidyalaya%20in%20Gandhi%20Nagar%2C%20following%20complaints%20by%20the%20families%20of%20the%20Class%209%20students.%20Police%20said%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%20by%20one%20of%20the%20students%2C%20Hema%20Gulati%20made%20the%20communal%20remarks%20on%20Wednesday.%20She%20made%20derogatory%20remarks%20on%20the%20Kaaba%20--%20the%20sacred%20stone%20building%20at%20Mecca%20--%20and%20the%20Quran%2C%20the%20complaint%20said.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20Partition%2C%20you%20did%20not%20go%20to%20Pakistan.%20You%20stayed%20in%20India.%20You%20have%20no%20contribution%20in%20India's%20freedom%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20quoted%20the%20teacher%20as%20saying.%20A%20copy%20of%20the%20complaint%20shows%20it%20was%20filed%20on%20Friday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20students'%20families%20have%20said%20such%20remarks%20can%20lead%20to%20discord%20in%20school%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20teacher%20be%20sacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20woman%2C%20whose%20two%20children%20study%20in%20the%20school%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20teacher%20goes%20unpunished%2C%20others%20will%20get%20emboldened.%20They%20should%20be%20told%20to%20just%20teach%20and%20not%20speak%20on%20matters%20about%20which%20they%20have%20no%20knowledge.%20There%20is%20no%20use%20of%20a%20teacher%20who%20creates%20differences%20among%20students.%20We%20demand%20that%20the%20teacher%20be%20removed%20from%20the%20school%2C%20she%20should%20not%20teach%20in%20any%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20MLA%20and%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20Anil%20Kumar%20Bajpai%20has%20slammed%20the%20teacher.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20absolutely%20wrong.%20The%20responsibility%20of%20a%20teacher%20is%20to%20give%20good%20education%20to%20the%20children.%20The%20teacher%20should%20not%20pass%20derogatory%20comments%20against%20any%20religious%20or%20holy%20place.%20Such%20people%20should%20be%20arrested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaints%20against%20the%20Delhi%20teacher%20come%20amid%20the%20outcry%20against%20Tripta%20Tyagi%20for%20putting%20a%20Muslim%20student%20through%20the%20traumatic%20experience%20of%20being%20slapped%20by%20his%20classmates.%20The%2060-year-old%20teacher%20has%20admitted%20that%20she%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20mistake%26quot%3B%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftripta-tyagi-neha-public-school-muzaffarnagar-i-made-a-mistake-but-theres-no-communal-angle-up-teacher-apologises-4335758%5C%22%3Estressed%20that%20she%20had%20no%20communal%20motive%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20police%20case%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20her%20and%20the%20boy's%20family%20has%20demanded%20strict%20action.%20The%20boy%2C%20shaken%20by%20what%20he%20went%20through%2C%20has%20now%20been%20shifted%20to%20another%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693285860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fkpqg78n8_school-generic_625x300_22_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-gandhi-nagar-sarvodaya-bal-vidyalaya-in-gandhi-nagar-hema-gulati-why-didnt-you-go-to-pak-delhi-teacher-charged-for-comments-in-class-4338256%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Four%20Muslim%20students%20of%20a%20Delhi%20school%20have%20alleged%20that%20their%20teacher%20made%20communal%20remarks%20and%20asked%20them%20why%20their%20families%20did%20not%20go%20to%20Pakistan%20during%20Partition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A138%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-gandhi-nagar-sarvodaya-bal-vidyalaya-in-gandhi-nagar-hema-gulati-why-didnt-you-go-to-pak-delhi-teacher-charged-for-comments-in-class-4338256%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-gandhi-nagar-sarvodaya-bal-vidyalaya-in-gandhi-nagar-hema-gulati-why-didnt-you-go-to-pak-delhi-teacher-charged-for-comments-in-class-4338256%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhi-gandhi-nagar-sarvodaya-bal-vidyalaya-in-gandhi-nagar-hema-gulati-why-didnt-you-go-to-pak-delhi-teacher-charged-for-comments-in-class-4338256%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Geetika%20Srivastava%20First%20Woman%20To%20Lead%20Indian%20Mission%20In%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGeetika%20Srivastava%20will%20be%20India's%20new%20charge%20d'affaires%20at%20its%20High%20Commission%20in%20Islamabad%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20woman%20to%20hold%20that%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20serving%20as%20joint%20secretary%20at%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%2C%20she%20will%20succeed%20Dr%20M%20Suresh%20Kumar%20who%20is%20likely%20to%20return%20to%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20job%20entails%20several%20responsibilities%2C%20a%20charge%20d'affaires%20is%20a%20diplomat%20who%20temporarily%20heads%20a%20diplomatic%20mission%20in%20a%20foreign%20country%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20Ambassador%20or%20High%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiplomatic%20missions%20between%20Commonwealth%20countries%20are%20called%20High%20Commissions%2C%20while%20those%20between%20non-Commonwealth%20countries%20are%20called%20Embassies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20and%20Pakistani%20missions%20in%20Islamabad%20and%20New%20Delhi%20have%20been%20without%20High%20Commissioners%20since%20August%202019%20and%20are%20being%20headed%20by%20their%20respective%20charge%20d'affaires.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjay%20Bisaria%20was%20the%20last%20Indian%20High%20Commissioner%20to%20Islamabad%20before%20Pakistan%20downgraded%20the%20status%20of%20the%20High%20Commission%20following%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%201947%2C%20when%20the%20late%20Sri%20Prakasa%20took%20charge%20as%20India's%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20there%20have%20been%2022%20heads%20of%20the%20mission.%20Ms%20Srivastava%2C%20a%202005%20Indian%20Foreign%20Service%20(IFS)%20officer%20will%20become%20the%20first%20woman%20in%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20High%20Commission%20in%20China%20from%202007%20to%202009%20and%20also%20had%20postings%20at%20the%20Regional%20Passport%20Office%20in%20Kolkata%20and%20as%20Director%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20division%20in%20the%20external%20affairs%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20diplomats%20from%20India%20have%20served%20in%20Pakistan%20previously%20but%20not%20in%20top%20positions%20such%20as%20this.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20role%20of%20a%20High%20Commissioner%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20besides%20the%20rigours%20of%20international%20diplomacy%2C%20especially%20between%20two%20countries%20that%20have%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20since%201947%2C%20comes%20with%20its%20unique%20set%20of%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamabad%20was%20designated%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-family%26quot%3B%20posting%20for%20Indian%20diplomats%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20limiting%20women%20officers%20from%20taking%20up%20the%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693285680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fm5i03