that%20the%20accused%20students%20had%20threatened%20him%20not%20to%20disclose%20the%20incident%20to%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20further%20alleged%20that%20around%2016%20days%20back%2C%20a%20student%20again%20tried%20to%20sexually%20assault%20him%20in%20the%20toilet.%20He%20has%20further%20stated%20that%20he%20had%20narrated%20the%20incident%20to%20two%20of%20his%20teachers%20in%20July%20and%20August%2C%20but%20they%20had%20asked%20him%20to%20not%20talk%20about%20the%20incident%20to%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDCW%20has%20sought%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20and%20Directorate%20of%20Education%20to%20provide%20a%20detailed%20action%20taken%20report%20on%20the%20two%20matters%20by%20September%201%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693282260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-08%2Fcpo0305o_delhi-police-generic_625x300_13_August_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F2-delhi-schoolboys-allege-sex-assault-during-summer-camp-probe-launched-4338002%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20government%20has%20set%20up%20an%20enquiry%20committee%20to%20probe%20the%20alleged%20sexual%20assault%20of%20two%20minor%20boys%20in%20a%20government%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F2-delhi-schoolboys-allege-sex-assault-during-summer-camp-probe-launched-4338002%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F2-delhi-schoolboys-allege-sex-assault-during-summer-camp-probe-launched-4338002%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2F2-delhi-schoolboys-allege-sex-assault-during-su