t%20Unpunished%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F25184020%2FIMG_0015.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20no%20place%20for%20the%20minorities.%20I%20fear%20for%20the%20future%20of%20a%20country%20that%20has%20declared%20war%20against%20a%20section%20of%20its%20people.%20I%20fear%20the%20dissolution%20of%20the%20Republic%20as%20our%20founding%20fathers%20had%20conceived%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20shared%20my%20misgivings%20with%20a%20dear%20friend%2C%20his%20glib%20response%20was%20that%20if%20the%20BJP%20loses%20the%202024%20general%20election%2C%20the%20cowardly%20saffron%20hordes%20will%20fade%20away%20into%20the%20woodwork%20and%20our%20bustling%2C%20chaotic%20democracy%20will%20once%20again%20reassert%20itself.%20The%20mistake%20he%20makes%20is%20in%20presuming%20that%20the%20colossal%20damage%20done%20to%20institutions%20and%20the%20social%20fabric%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%20stems%20purely%20from%20politics%20and%20will%20be%20mended%20once%20the%20authoritarian%20ruler%20and%20his%20minions%20are%20booted%20out%2C%20bag%20and%20baggage%2C%20the%20way%20the%20dictator%20and%20her%20hoodlums%20were%20after%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20my%20simple-minded%20buddy%20has%20ignored%20is%20that%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20there%20has%20been%20a%20frontal%20assault%20on%20our%20culture%2C%20of%20which%20politics%20is%20only%20one%20component.%20This%20regime%20%E2%80%95%20a%20gravedigger%20of%20culture%2C%20no%20less%20%E2%80%95%20has%20consciously%20divided%20us%20on%20religious%20lines%20and%20attacked%20lifestyles%2C%20traditions%2C%20art%2C%20learning%2C%20our%20collective%20memory%2C%20even%20how%20we%20love%20one%20another.%20It%20has%20devastated%20the%20very%20idea%20of%20a%20multicultural%20ethos%20based%20on%20liberal%20humanism%20that%20our%20founding%20fathers%20had%20conceived%2C%20and%20which%20was%20hitherto%20a%20stop-start%20work%20in%20progress.%20The%20damage%20inflicted%20seems%20irreparable.%20But%20I%20am%20getting%20ahead%20of%20the%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20generation%20of%20midnight%E2%80%99s%20children%20grew%20up%20at%20a%20time%20when%20we%20willed%20ourselves%20to%20celebrate%20our%20common%20nationhood.%20%E2%80%98Unity%20in%20diversity%E2%80%99%20was%20the%20hopeful%20shibboleth%20by%20which%20we%20defined%20our%20priceless%20heritage%20of%20religions%2C%20languages%2C%20ethnicities.%20%E2%80%9CAmar%2C%20Akbar%2C%20Antony%E2%80%9D%20were%20catchwords%20that%20represented%20our%20collective%20aspiration%20for%20brotherhood%20by%20setting%20aside%20our%20differences.%20Our%20founding%20fathers%20spun%20the%20enchanting%20myth%20that%20we%20are%20a%20tolerant%2C%20non-violent%20people%2C%20in%20the%20hope%20that%2C%20although%20blood-soaked%20at%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20birth%2C%20we%20would%20endeavour%20to%20live%20up%20to%20the%20Nehruvian%20idea%20of%20a%20modern%2C%20inclusive%20democracy%20of%20religious%20tolerance%20and%20cultural%20pluralism.%20That%20ideal%20lies%20in%20tatters%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20road%20to%20freedom%20was%20besmirched%20by%20unspeakable%20inhumanity%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20border%20as%20man%20killed%20man%20in%20a%20crazed%20religious%20frenzy.%20In%20lieu%20of%20gas%20chambers%20but%20equally%20productive%2C%20ordinary%20citizens%20brandishing%20swords%2C%20butchers%E2%80%99%20knives%2C%20guns%20and%20even%20their%20bare%20hands%2C%20went%20on%20a%20killing%20spree%20in%20a%20collective%20state%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthoughtlessness%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20term%20used%20by%20Hannah%20Arendt%20to%20describe%20the%20irrationality%20of%20the%20unspeakable%20evil%20committed%20by%20the%20Nazis.%20It%20is%20estimated%20that%20up%20to%202%20million%20men%2C%20women%20and%20children%20were%20butchered%20and%2020%20million%20people%20displaced%20in%20the%20holocaust%20of%20Partition.%20And%20there%20was%20no%20retribution%20for%20such%20evil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Solzhenitsyn%20had%20observed%20with%20devastating%20prescience%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20we%20neither%20punish%20nor%20reproach%20evildoers%2C%20we%20are%20ripping%20the%20foundations%20of%20justice%20from%20future%20generations.%E2%80%9D%20While%20the%20Nazis%20were%20hunted%20down%20and%20made%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20crimes%2C%20the%20millions%20of%20killers%20and%20their%20abettors%20during%20Partition%20quietly%20returned%20as%20anonymous%20lawful%20citizens%20of%20the%20two%20newly%20independent%20nations.%20It%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20infer%20that%20these%20criminals%20slipped%20back%20to%20their%20everyday%20roles%20as%20teachers%2C%20workers%2C%20maulvis%2C%20sadhus%2C%20government%20employees%20and%20what%20have%20you%3B%20but%20by%20letting%20these%20murderous%20vectors%20of%20hate%20go%20scot-free%20without%20even%20so%20much%20as%20a%20condemnation%20of%20their%20bestiality%2C%20there%20has%20been%20neither%20repentance%20nor%20redemptive%20change.%20(Is%20it%20any%20surprise%20that%20this%20regime%20that%20has%20fattened%20on%20hatred%2C%20has%20declared%20August%2014th%20as%20Partition%20Horrors%20Remembrance%20Day%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20alive%20the%20fratricidal%20bitterness%3F%20With%20like%20intent%2C%20the%20film%20Kashmir%20Files%20that%20spews%20venom%20against%20the%20Muslim%20community%20has%20been%20bestowed%20the%20Nargis%20Dutt%20Award%20for%20Best%20Film%20on%20National%20Integration%20at%20the%2069th%20National%20Film%20Awards.)%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20miasma%20of%20distrust%20and%20hate%20engendered%20by%20Partition%20suppurated%20in%20these%20diseased%20souls%20out%20of%20the%20public%20eye%2C%20ready%20to%20strike%20when%20the%20time%20was%20ripe.%20The%20Partition%20savagery%20provided%20the%20template%20for%20the%20mass%20killings%20in%20Delhi%20in%201984%2C%20in%20Mumbai%20in%201992-93%2C%20in%20Gujarat%20in%202002%20and%20myriads%20of%20lesser%20conflagrations.%20In%20no%20other%20country%20on%20earth%20have%20civilians%20killed%20their%20fellow%20beings%20in%20such%20monstrous%20numbers%20and%20with%20such%20frequency.%20We%20are%20undoubtedly%20among%20the%20cruellest%20people%20on%20earth!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20of%20the%20religious%20bigotry%20plaguing%20this%20country%20were%20planted%20a%20century%20ago.%20As%20far%20back%20as%201921%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20at%20its%20very%20inception%20pronounced%20that%20that%20Hindus%20need%20a%20separate%20nation%20and%20Muslims%20must%20be%20denied%20any%20rights%20in%20it.%20This%20fuzzy%20notion%20of%20Hindu%20nationalism%20was%20formalised%20by%20VD%20Savarkar%20as%20an%20exclusivist%20and%20homogenising%20doctrine%20called%20Hindutva%20that%20is%20underpinned%20by%20an%20obsessive%2C%20visceral%20hatred%20of%20Muslims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F07%2F15155952%2Fhindu-mahasbha.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20photo%20of%20Hindu%20Mahasabha.%20Standing%20-%20Shankar%20Kistaiya%2C%20Gopal%20Godse%2C%20Madanlal%20Pahwa%2C%20Digambar%20Badge.%20Seated%20-%20Narayan%20Apte%2C%20Vinayak%20D.%20Savarkar%2C%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20Vishnu%20Karkare.%20Credit%3A%20Flickr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-163350%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22571%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGroup%20photo%20of%20Hindu%20Mahasabha.%20Standing%20%E2%80%93%20Shankar%20Kistaiya%2C%20Gopal%20Godse%2C%20Madanlal%20Pahwa%2C%20Digambar%20Badge.%20Seated%20%E2%80%93%20Narayan%20Apte%2C%20Vinayak%20D.%20Savarkar%2C%20Nathuram%20Godse%2C%20Vishnu%20Karkare.%20Credit%3A%20Flickr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20decades%2C%20behind%20the%20benign%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20nurturing%20Bharatiya%20culture%2C%20ethnocentric%20Hindutva%20has%20spread%20across%20the%20land%20through%20the%20furtive%20but%20relentless%20RSS%20machinery.%20Millions%20of%20young%20and%20old%20in%20Shishu%20Mandirs%2C%20Vidya%20Bharati%20schools%20and%20the%20ubiquitous%20shakhas%20across%20the%20country%20have%20been%20tutored%20in%20a%20hyper-nationalism%20that%20fosters%20an%20implacable%20hatred%20of%20Muslims%20who%20must%20pay%20for%20historical%20wrongs%20committed%20against%20Hindus.%20Even%20the%20Amar%20Chitra%20Katha%20comic%20series%20are%20exploited%20for%20propaganda%20and%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccultural%E2%80%9D%20conditioning%20of%20minds%20in%20what%20Sumit%20Sarkar%20terms%20%E2%80%9Ca%20Gramscian%20process%20of%20building%20up%20hegemony%20through%20molecular%20permeation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20saffron%20brigade%20has%20succeeded%20in%20capturing%20the%20collective%20consciousness%20of%20a%20large%20section%20of%20Hindus%20and%20indoctrinating%20them%20in%20the%20gospel%20of%20Hindutva.%20A%20study%20across%20four%20states%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20Developing%20Societies%20in%202019%20showed%20that%2072%25%20of%20Indians%20had%20clear%20majoritarian%20views%20on%20issues%20relating%20to%20banning%20beef%2C%20religious%20conversions%2C%20love%20jihad%20etc.%20Since%20then%2C%20their%20numbers%20could%20only%20have%20grown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20we%20see%20today%20is%20Hindutva%20with%20a%20swagger.%20In%20January%20this%20year%20Mohan%20Bhagwat%2C%20the%20reigning%20pontiff%20of%20Hindutva%2C%20publicly%20enunciated%20the%20Hindutva%20doctrine%20with%20staggering%20bluntness.%20In%20a%20textbook%20case%20of%20hate%20speech%2C%20he%20brazenly%20stated%20that%20Hindu%20society%20had%20finally%20awakened%20after%20being%20at%20war%20for%20over%201%2C000%20years%20and%20is%20now%20ready%20to%20do%20battle%20to%20defend%20Hindu%20society%2C%20Hindu%20Dharma%20and%20Hindu%20culture%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20against%20an%20enemy%20without%20but%20against%20an%20enemy%20within.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20same%20breath%2C%20he%20warned%20Muslims%20to%20%E2%80%9Cabandon%20their%20boisterous%20rhetoric%20of%20supremacy%E2%80%9D%2C%20leaving%20no%20doubt%20whom%20he%20considered%20the%20enemy.%20And%20for%20good%20measure%2C%20he%20reiterated%20the%20majoritarian%20trope%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20simple%20truth%20is%20this%3A%20Hindustan%20(the%20land%20of%20the%20Hindus)%20should%20remain%20Hindustan%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20unspoken%20implication%20being%20that%20minorities%20live%20here%20on%20sufferance.%20There%20was%20no%20public%20outrage%20as%20he%20was%20merely%20articulating%20this%20majoritarian%20government%E2%80%99s%20creed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20undeniable%20that%20in%20the%20two%20largest%20democracies%2C%20the%20invasion%20of%20neo-Nazis%2C%20supremacists%20and%20extreme%20right-wing%20nationalists%20into%20the%20mainstream%20of%20political%20and%20cultural%20discourse%20has%20coincided%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20Modi%20and%20Trump.%20There%20is%20an%20eerie%20similarity%20in%20the%20concepts%20deployed%20by%20their%20advocates%20to%20foment%20fear%20and%20loathing%20among%20their%20constituents.%20The%20toxic%20disinformation%20regarding%20an%20embattled%20white%20majority%20population%20being%20overwhelmed%20by%20immigrants%20is%20twinned%20with%20the%20criminal%20predisposition%20of%20immigrants.%20This%20is%20matched%20by%20the%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20propaganda%20of%20disproportionate%20increase%20in%20the%20Muslim%20population%2C%20their%20enticement%20of%20Hindu%20women%20through%20love%20jihad%2C%20their%20food%20jihad%20and%20the%20enduring%20theme%20of%20their%20disloyalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20whereas%20the%20white%20supremacists%E2%80%99%20strategy%20of%20expanding%20their%20base%20is%20limited%20to%20tapping%20potential%20fellow-travellers%20and%20sneaking%20into%20mainstream%20media%20and%20political%20debate%2C%20the%20majoritarian%20nationalism%20in%20our%20midst%20that%20is%20on%20a%20crusade%20against%20Muslims%2C%20Christians%20and%20anything%20or%20anybody%20perceived%20as%20inimical%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20project%2C%20has%20now%20spread%20its%20tentacles%20everywhere.%20With%20its%20arsenal%20of%20zealous%20mobs%2C%20Goebbelsian%20propaganda%2C%20media%20lapdogs%2C%20infiltrated%20institutions%2C%20inexhaustible%20funds%20et%20al.%2C%20it%20has%20captured%20the%20social%20space.%20Manipur%20and%20Nuh%20are%20a%20foretaste%20of%20things%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20staring%20into%20the%20abyss!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMathew%20John%20is%20a%20former%20civil%20servant.%20Views%20are%20personal.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693280234000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F25184020%2FIMG_0015.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-manipur-nuh-ethnic-violence-partition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20its%20arsenal%20of%20zealous%20mobs%2C%20Goebbelsian%20propaganda%2C%20media%20lapdogs%2C%20infiltrated%20institutions%2C%20inexhaustible%20funds%20et%20al.%2C%20it%20has%20captured%20the%20social%20space.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-manipur-nuh-ethnic-violence-partition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Guatemala%20body%20ratifies%20presidential%20vote%20result%20amid%20new%20bid%20to%20thwart%20victor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693279889000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103155533%2Cimgsize-22600.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fguatemala-body-ratifies-presidential-vote-result-amid-new-bid-to-thwart-victor%2Farticleshow%2F103155092.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103155092.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBernardo%20Arevalo's%20victory%20in%20Guatemala's%20presidential%20election%20has%20been%20ratified%20by%20the%20supreme%20electoral%20tribunal%2C%20despite%20a%20new%20attempt%20to%20suspend%20his%20party.%20Arevalo%2C%20a%20center-left%20candidate%2C%20won%20the%20second-round%20run-off%20in%20August%2C%20but%20his%20party%20Semilla%20faced%20threats%20of%20exclusion%20from%20the%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fguatemala-body-ratifies-presidential-vote-result-amid-new-bid-to-thwart-victor%2Farticleshow%2F103155092.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fguatemala-body-ratifies-presidential-vote-result-amid-new-bid-to-thwart-victor%2Famp_articleshow%2F103155092.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fguatemala-body-ratifies-presidential-vote-result-amid-new-bid-to-thwart-victor%2Famp_articleshow%2F103155092.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Five%20Takeaways%20From%20the%20BRICS%20Expansion%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29085027%2FF4StBG3WEAAghXF.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expansion%20of%20BRICS%20to%20include%20four%20West%20Asian%20nations%20along%20with%20two%20other%20influential%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20one%20African%20and%20the%20other%20South%20American%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20a%20head%20turner%2C%20given%20the%20current%20geopolitical%20fluidity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20are%20expected%20to%20accept%20the%20invitation%20to%20join%20though%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20injected%20a%20note%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20the%20process%2C%20saying%20it%20will%20%E2%80%9Cconsider%E2%80%9D%20the%20invitation%20and%20make%20%E2%80%9Can%20appropriate%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20takeaways%20from%20the%20summit%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisillusionment%20with%20the%20US%2FWest%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20membership%20of%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Iran%2C%20UAE%20and%20Egypt%20%E2%80%93%20Ethiopia%20and%20Argentina%20are%20the%20two%20other%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20in%20BRICS%20will%20take%20effect%20from%20January%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20enthusiasm%20for%20BRICS%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region%20signals%20that%20it%20no%20longer%20sees%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20world%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20weakening%20US%20influence%20in%20the%20region%20became%20apparent%20with%20the%20China-brokered%20Saudi-Iran%20peace%20deal%20earlier%20this%20year.%20Barring%20Iran%2C%20each%20of%20these%20nations%20has%20been%20a%20close%20US%20ally%20until%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20disillusionment%20with%20the%20US%20may%20have%20begun%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20ago.%20During%20the%20Arab%20Spring%2C%20the%20Obama%20administration%E2%80%99s%20abandonment%20of%20close%20ally%20Hosni%20Mubarak%20was%20a%20rude%20awakening%20for%20other%20long%20standing%20American%20friends%20and%20partners%20from%20Saudi%20to%20Bahrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20George%20Bush%E2%80%99s%202003%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%20and%20the%20overthrow%20of%20Saddam%20Hussein%E2%80%99s%20Baath%20regime%20strengthened%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20clout%20in%20the%20Shia-majority%20country%20and%20in%20the%20region.%20Eight%20years%20later%2C%20the%20Saudis%20and%20the%20Gulf%20Co-operation%20Council%E2%80%99s%20Persian%20Shield%20army%20had%20to%20rush%20to%20the%20rescue%20of%20the%20Sunni%20rulers%20of%20Shia-majority%20Bahrain%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20a%20nascent%20%E2%80%9CArab%20Spring%E2%80%9D%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Obama%20administration%E2%80%99s%20pivot%20to%20Asia%2C%20and%20engagement%20with%20Iran%20for%20a%20nuclear%20deal%20convinced%20Riyadh%20that%20the%20US%20focus%20had%20moved%20to%20the%20Asia-Pacific.%20President%20Donald%20Trump%E2%80%99s%20tough%20talk%20against%20Iran%20rekindled%20Saudi%20hope%20in%20its%20benefactor%2C%20only%20for%20it%20to%20shatter%20when%20Washington%20did%20nothing%20to%20help%20as%20missiles%20fired%20by%20Iran-backed%20Houthi%20rebels%20struck%20two%20of%20its%20refineries%20halting%20production%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20looking%20at%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20the%20region.%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20UAE%20%5Bjoining%20BRICS%5D%20is%20symbolic%20of%20the%20disenchantment%20of%20the%20West%20Asian%20countries%20with%20the%20US%20as%20a%20security%20provider%20in%20the%20region%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Talmiz%20Ahmed%2C%20who%20was%20India%E2%80%99s%20ambassador%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Oman%20and%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20plus%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20younger%20leadership%2C%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20in%20Saudi%2C%20and%20Mohammed%20bin%20Zayed%20in%20UAE%2C%20have%20marked%20what%20Ahmed%20called%20%E2%80%9Ca%20coming%20of%20age%20moment%20for%20these%20two%20countries%2C%20a%20return%20of%20national%20self-confidence%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20major%20oil%20producing%20countries%20had%20decided%20to%20find%20their%20own%20place%20in%20the%20world%20in%20pursuit%20of%20their%20own%20interests%2C%20said%20Ahmed.%20Riyadh%20has%20more%20strategic%20ambitions%20than%20the%20UAE%20and%20wants%20to%20wield%20more%20influence%20on%20its%20own%2C%20on%20the%20global%20stage%2C%20while%20the%20UAE%20is%20focussed%20on%20pushing%20its%20commercial%20interests.%20Countries%20in%20West%20Asia%20%E2%80%9Cwant%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20East%20Asian%20success%20story%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20former%20ambassador%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-brics-22-countries-expansion-stakes%5C%22%3EAs%20BRICS%20Evolves%20Criteria%20for%20Expansion%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20India%20Thinks%20of%20the%2022%20Countries%20That%20Want%20to%20Join%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIran%20less%20isolated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20membership%20of%20BRICS%20gives%20Iran%20an%20opportunity%20to%20signal%20that%20the%20US%20attempt%20to%20isolate%20it%20has%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20forged%20close%20ties%20with%20China%20(the%20two%20sides%20have%20reportedly%20signed%20a%20%E2%80%9C25-year%20co-operation%20programme%E2%80%9D)%20and%20Russia.%20With%20Chinese%20mediation%2C%20Iran%20signed%20a%20peace%20agreement%20with%20Saudi.%20The%20deal%20has%20stopped%20the%20fighting%20in%20Yemen%2C%20though%20the%20conflict%20in%20that%20country%20still%20awaits%20resolution.%20Iran%20has%20supplied%20Russia%20with%20several%20hundred%20attack%20and%20surveillance%20drones%20for%20its%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20By%20mid-2023%2C%20the%20drones%20were%20being%20manufactured%20in%20Russia%20with%20Iranian%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Ebrahim%20Raisi%2C%20an%20anti-west%20hardliner%2C%20told%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20that%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20the%20grouping%20would%20bring%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20benefits%E2%80%9D.%20Under%20UN%20sanctions%20for%20much%20of%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20Iran%20has%20been%20an%20early%20votary%20of%20%E2%80%9Cde-dollarisation%E2%80%9D%20or%20trade%20in%20local%20currencies.%20On%20returning%20to%20Tehran%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.al-monitor.com%2Foriginals%2F2023%2F08%2Fraisi-pushes-anti-us-agenda-brics-iran-celebrates-ascension%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Islamic%2520Republic%2520hopes%2520that%2Cinfluence%2520in%2520the%2520global%2520sphere.%26amp%3Btext%3DIran%2527s%2520President%2520Ebrahim%2520Raisi%2520told%2Cdollar%2520in%2520their%2520economic%2520dealings%5C%22%3ERaisi%20told%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Iran%E2%80%99s%20entry%20into%20BRICS%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20random%20occurrence%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20%E2%80%9Ca%20policy%20pursued%20by%20the%20government%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20well-oiled%20BRICS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grouping%20now%20has%20five%20of%20the%20top%2010%20oil%20producing%20countries%2C%20adding%20to%20its%20financial%20and%20economic%20heft.%20Saudi%20and%20founding%20members%20Russia%20and%20Brazil%20are%20respectively%20the%20second%2C%20third%20and%20eighth%20biggest%20oil%20producing%20countries%20(the%20US%20tops%20the%20list)%2C%20while%20UAE%20and%20Iran%20are%20ranked%20seventh%20and%20ninth%20respectively.%20The%20three%20West%20Asian%20countries%20are%20key%20members%20of%20OPEC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20this%20will%20play%20out%20for%20oil%20production%20and%20prices%20versus%20demand%20is%20to%20be%20seen.%20What%20is%20apparent%20since%20last%20year%20is%20that%20Saudi%20has%20ignored%20repeated%20US%20calls%20not%20to%20cut%20production%20as%20it%20would%20blunt%20the%20impact%20of%20sanctions%20on%20Moscow.%20Instead%2C%20Saudi%20has%20cooperated%20with%20Russia%20in%20OPEC%2B%20to%20do%20exactly%20this%20in%20order%20to%20prop%20up%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20reached%20yet%20another%20agreement%20to%20deepen%20production%20cuts%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20increase%20prices%2C%20which%20have%20remained%20low%20due%20to%20sluggish%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Asian%20presence%20in%20BRICS%20puts%20the%20OPEC%20big%20shots%20in%20the%20same%20room%20as%20big%20oil%20consumers.%20Despite%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20determined%20push%20to%20replace%20fossil%20fuels%20with%20renewables%2C%20accelerated%20by%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20despite%20the%20slowing%20down%20of%20the%20Chinese%20economy%2C%20China%20along%20with%20India%20will%20remain%20among%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20oil%20consumers%20for%20the%20next%20few%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20expected%20that%20Saudi%20will%20seek%20more%20clout%20within%20the%20grouping%20with%20investment%20in%20the%20BRICS%20bank%2C%20called%20the%20National%20Development%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBRICS%20and%20blocs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20BRICS%20emphasise%20that%20it%20is%20not%20an%20anti-Western%20bloc%2C%20and%20speak%20about%20%E2%80%9Cstrategic%20autonomy%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20multipolarity%2C%20and%20having%20their%20voice%20heard%20in%20the%20global%20arena.%20This%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20main%20attraction%20for%20the%20long%20waiting%20list%20for%20joining%20it%2C%20at%20last%20count%2040%20countries.%20Access%20to%20China%20is%20always%20good%20leverage%20in%20negotiations%20with%20the%20West.%C2%A0%20Interestingly%20though%2C%20the%20summit%20declaration%20affirmed%20the%20importance%20of%20US-Iran%20efforts%20to%20restore%20the%202015%20nuclear%20deal%20(or%20Joint%20Comprehensive%20Plan%20of%20Action)%20%E2%80%9Cand%20hope%20for%20relevant%20parties%20to%20restore%20the%20full%20and%20effective%20implementation%20of%20the%20JCPOA%20at%20an%20early%20date%E2%80%9D%2C%20appearing%20to%20distance%20itself%20from%20President%20Raisi%E2%80%99s%20belief%20that%20the%20US%20had%20nothing%20more%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20reality%20is%20also%20that%20two%20powerful%20BRICS%20members%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%2C%20are%20locked%20in%20adversarial%20relations%20with%20the%20US.%20And%20the%20queue%20to%20join%20the%20grouping%20is%20a%20validation%20that%20they%20still%20carry%20enough%20influence%20in%20the%20world%20for%20these%20countries%20to%20want%20to%20associate%20with%20them.%20Inevitably%2C%20BRICS%20will%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20anti-US%2Fanti-west%20bloc%20in%20the%20same%20way%20that%20China%20sees%20the%20Quad%20as%20a%20US-led%20%E2%80%9Csmall%20circle%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20an%20attempt%20to%20create%20Cold%20war-style%20camps%20and%20an%20%E2%80%9CAsian%20NATO%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%E2%80%99s%20excellent%20ties%20with%20each%20of%20the%20BRICS%20members%2C%20including%20the%20new%20ones%2C%20the%20technology%20boost%20of%20Chandrayaan%20-3%E2%80%99s%20moon%20landing%20during%20the%20summit%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20demography%20and%20its%20growing%20economy%2C%20all%20give%20it%20influence%20in%20the%20group%20potentially%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20turning%20into%20an%20anti-West%20bloc.%20But%20as%20the%20most%20powerful%20country%20in%20BRICS%2C%20China%20dominates%20the%20grouping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20West%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20membership%20of%20BRICS%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20oddity%20for%20a%20country%20that%20is%20in%20a%20deep%20and%20nationally%20celebrated%20embrace%20with%20the%20US.%20But%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20aspiration%20to%20be%20accepted%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CGlobal%20South%E2%80%9D%20and%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20quest%20for%20a%20permanent%20seat%20at%20the%20United%20Nations%20Security%20Council%20are%20clearly%20better%20served%20by%20multilateralism%20of%20the%20BRICS%20kind%2C%20even%20if%20China%20is%20the%20dominant%20player.%20The%20summit%20declaration%20contains%20an%20unequivocal%20paragraph%20on%20supporting%20the%20claims%20of%20India%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20Brazil%20for%20%E2%80%9Ca%20greater%20role%20in%20international%20affairs%2C%20in%20particular%20in%20the%20United%20Nations%2C%20including%20its%20Security%20Council%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20also%20used%20BRICS%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Shanghai%20Co-operation%20Organisation%20to%20keep%20lines%20open%20to%20Beijing%20for%20a%20diplomatic%20resolution%20of%20the%20LAC%20dispute%2C%20however%20dim%20the%20chances%20look%20for%20a%20return%20to%20the%20status%20quo%20of%20April%202020.%20The%20Modi-Xi%20meeting%20on%20the%20summit%E2%80%99s%20sidelines%20had%20no%20breakthroughs%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManaging%20differences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMost%20commentary%20on%20BRICS%20describe%20it%20as%20a%20grouping%20that%20lacks%20inner%20cohesion%2C%20and%20note%20that%20it%20will%20remain%20hobbled%20by%20adversarial%20relations%20between%20India%20and%20China.%20The%20same%20could%20be%20said%20of%20G20%20with%20Russia%20and%20China%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20Western%20members%20of%20the%20grouping.%20At%20the%20recent%20summit%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%20BRICS%20was%20able%20to%20manage%20its%20differences%20to%20agree%20on%20admitting%20six%20new%20members.%20It%20also%20put%20out%20a%20communique%20acceptable%20to%20all%20including%20India%2C%20that%20the%20more%20powerful%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccohesive%E2%80%9D%20G20%20may%20yet%20fail%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%20the%20BRICS%20document%20skipped%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20entirely%2C%20and%20instead%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cconcern%20at%20%E2%80%9Congoing%20conflicts%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20formulation%20that%20would%20not%20pass%20muster%20in%20most%20other%20multilateral%20fora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Johannesburg%20Declaration%20does%20refer%20to%20G%2020%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpremier%20multilateral%20forum%20in%20the%20field%20of%20international%20economic%20and%20financial%20cooperation%20that%20comprises%20both%20developed%20and%20emerging%20markets%20and%20developing%20countries%20where%20major%20economies%20jointly%20seek%20solutions%20to%20global%20challenges%E2%80%9D.%20In%20a%20good%20augury%20for%20India%2C%20the%20BRICS%20summit%20said%20it%20looked%20forward%20to%20%E2%80%9Ca%20successful%20hosting%20of%20the%2018th%20G20%20Summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20under%20the%20Indian%20G20%20Presidency%E2%80%9D%20boosting%20hopes%20that%20there%20might%20be%20consensus%20on%20the%20Delhi%20Declaration%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20data-tooltip%3D%5C%22Show%20trimmed%20content%5C%22%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENirupama%20Subramanian%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693279342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F29085027%2FF4StBG3WEAAghXF.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbrics-expansion-saudi-arabia-oil-iran%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20enthusiasm%20for%20BRICS%20in%20the%20West%20Asian%20region%20signals%20that%20it%20no%20longer%20sees%20its%20relationship%20with%20the%20world%20through%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20United%20States.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fbrics-expansion-saudi-arabia-oil-iran%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian-American%20Nikki%20Haley%20raises%20%241%20million%20in%20less%20than%20three%20days%20after%20GOP%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693279196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103154572%2Cimgsize-1349508.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-american-nikki-haley-raises-usd-1-million-in-less-than-three-days-after-gop-debate%2Farticleshow%2F103154469.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103154469.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-american-nikki-haley-raises-usd-1-million-i