0phenomenon%20not%20just%20in%20the%20history%20of%20that%20north-eastern%20border%20state%20but%20also%20in%20India.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20decision%20of%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Governor%20Anusuiya%20Uikey%2C%20and%20then%20of%20the%20Business%20Advisory%20Committee%20of%20the%20Manipur%20assembly%2C%20to%20%3Cspan%3Ecall%20for%20a%20regular%20session%20of%20the%20assembly%20with%20just%20one%20sitting%2C%20however%2C%20has%20all%20the%20signs%20of%20a%20move%20made%20only%20to%20send%20out%20a%20message%20that%20the%20state%20is%20functional%2C%20lest%20the%20demand%20from%20the%20opposition%20to%20clamp%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20a%20Bharatiya-Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-ruled%20%E2%80%98double-engine%E2%80%99%20state%20gets%20a%20boost.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20constitutional%20requirement%2C%20there%20has%20to%20be%20an%20assembly%20session%20every%20six%20months%2C%20unless%20there%20is%20direct%20rule%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20that%20particular%20state.%20The%20last%20session%20in%20Manipur%20was%20held%20in%20the%20first%20week%20of%20March%2C%20meaning%20that%20by%20the%20first%20week%20of%20September%2C%20the%20governor%20has%20to%20call%20the%20next%20session%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20his%20cabinet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20governor%20Uikey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-assembly-special-session-anusuiya-uikey-biren%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20heed%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20formal%20request%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hold%20the%20session%20initially%2C%20she%20eventually%20did%2C%20leaving%20one%20to%20only%20conclude%20that%20she%20must%20have%20done%20so%20at%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Union%20to%20ensure%20that%20a%20BJP-ruled%20state%20is%20not%20seen%20hurtling%20towards%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20constitutional%20aberration%20of%20holding%20a%20single%20sitting%20of%20a%20regular%20assembly%20session%20in%20Manipur%20is%2C%20however%2C%20only%20a%20continuation%20of%20what%20governors%20appointed%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20are%20increasingly%20seen%20to%20be%20doing%20in%20several%20states%20%E2%80%93%20going%20against%20the%20norm.%20The%20phenomenon%20is%20noticed%20both%20in%20BJP%20and%20opposition-ruled%20states.%20If%20we%20focus%20on%20the%20details%2C%20each%20instance%20comes%20across%20more%20as%20an%20act%20by%20a%20political%20appointee%20than%20intended%20to%20protect%20the%20constitution%20which%20the%20governors%20are%20expected%20to%20safeguard%20in%20each%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPunjab%20assembly%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETake%20the%20case%20of%20Punjab.%20Governor%20Banwarilal%20Purohit%20is%20taking%20on%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Punjab%2C%20an%20opposition-ruled%20state%2C%20based%20on%20his%20allegation%20that%20the%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20government%20is%20facilitating%20the%20drug%20menace%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Feditorials%2Frespect-the-constitution-101693188988916.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3Dhurt%2520India%2527s%2520democracy.-%2CArticle%2520356%2520should%2520only%2520be%2520reserved%2520as%2520a%2520last%2520resort%2Cmore%2520respectful%2520of%2520other%2520authorities%5C%22%3Egovernor%20is%20threatening%20to%20recommend%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20over%20the%20the%20chief%20minister%20not%20responding%20on%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20interesting%20is%20this%20threat%20of%20the%20governor%20to%20recommend%20President%E2%80%99s%20Rule%20in%20Punjab%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Union%20has%20doggedly%20refused%20to%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Manipur%20even%20after%20at%20least%20150%20people%20have%20lost%20lives%20in%20an%20ethnic%20conflict%2C%20leaving%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20in%20relief%20camps%20since%20May%20and%20voices%20from%20within%20both%20Kukis%20and%20Meiteis%20demanding%20the%20accountability%20of%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%2C%20with%20some%20even%20demanding%20his%20resignation%20for%20failing%20to%20maintain%20law%20and%20order.%20Importantly%2C%20thousands%20of%20arms%20were%20looted%20from%20police%20stations%20to%20kill%20innocent%20people.%20In%20Manipur%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20also%20the%20state%20home%20minister.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Punjab%20governor%E2%80%99s%20threat%20particularly%20strikes%20as%20odd%20when%20you%20also%20take%20into%20cognisance%20that%20an%20affidavit%20was%20filed%20in%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20in%202020%20by%20a%20state%20police%20officer%20handling%20the%20anti-drug%20drive%20stating%20that%20the%20BJP%20chief%20minister%20had%20categorically%20asked%20her%20to%20go%20slow%20in%20some%20drug-related%20cases.%20No%20action%20was%20seen%20taken%20on%20that%20front%20either%20by%20the%20then%20state%20governor%20nor%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETamil%20Nadu%20assembly%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELook%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20After%20a%20face-off%20with%20the%20NSCN%20(Isak-Muivah)%20leaders%2C%20and%20several%20minor%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20state%20government%20led%20by%20BJP-ally%20National%20Democratic%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(NDPP)%2C%20the%20Centre%20removed%20Nagaland%20governor%20R.N.%20Ravi%20from%20his%20position%20and%20also%20as%20its%20interlocutor%20for%20the%20Indo-Naga%20peace%20talks%20in%202021.%20It%20also%20transferred%20him%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Raj%20Bhavan%20from%20the%20Kohima%20Raj%20Bhavan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERavi%2C%20as%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%2C%20has%20since%20been%20acting%20more%20like%20a%20political%20appointee%20than%20going%20by%20the%20constitutional%20rulebook.%20One%20such%20aberration%20was%20regularly%20blocking%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20assembly.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20he%20claimed%20in%20an%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20no%20bills%20were%20pending%20before%20him%20unlike%20what%20was%20claimed%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20M.K.%20Stalin%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Fthirteen-bills-pending-before-tn-governor-despite-his-earlier-claims%2Famp%5C%22%3Ean%20RTI%20reply%20recently%20revealed%20as%20many%20as%2013%20bills%20have%20been%20pending%20before%20him%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20January%2C%20Ravi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftamil-nadu%2Ftn-governor-skips-reference-to-dravidian-leaders-dravidian-model-of-government-in-his-assembly-address%2Farticle66355909.ece%3F_gl%3D1*42b503*_ga*VHFia0huSmJndExEMm1ydU5vR2JyZjFqS0dqRkRnR3NRZGd6RmpOZnc4VDBWM1hRWkFJMVRKTEZaMHBVbC13Ng%5C%22%3Ehit%20the%20headlines%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20Tamil%20Nadu%20governor%20to%20refuse%20to%20read%20a%20portion%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20text%20of%20his%20customary%20address%20to%20the%20assembly%20put%20together%20by%20the%20DMK%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20an%20aberration%20that%20took%20place%20also%20in%20the%20Kerala%20assembly%20in%202018%2C%20carried%20out%20by%20another%20Modi%20government%20appointed%20governor%20in%20the%20Left-ruled%20Kerala.%20In%20that%20southern%20state%20too%2C%20the%20current%20governor%20Arif%20Mohammad%20Khan%20has%20been%20following%20the%20same%20script%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fkerala%2Fkerala-governor-arif-mohammed-khan-press-conference-in-thiruvananthapuram-on-september-19-2022%2Farticle65909682.ece%2Famp%2F%5C%22%3Econtinuously%20taking%20on%20the%20opposition-ruled%20state%20government%20on%20some%20trivial%20matter