eatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20went%20like%20something%20along%20the%20lines%20of%2C%20%26quot%3BSo%20each%20planet%20has%20seven%20levels%2C%20and%20at%20first%20you%20can%20upgrade%20them%20with%20coins%2C%20but%20eventually%2C%20you'll%20probably%20want%20to%20start%20using%20labs.%20But%20I%20wouldn't%20worry%20about%20that%20right%20now%2C%20because%20you%20can't%20use%20labs%20or%20epics%20until%20you%20get%20more%20levels%20and%20planets%20anyway%E2%80%A6%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20started%20using%20it%2C%20I%20was%20swamped%20by%20the%20game's%20features%2C%20which%20feature%20little%20explanation%20and%20include%20%26quot%3Bepics%26quot%3B%20where%20you%20work%20together%20with%20other%20players%20to%20meet%20goals%2C%20%26quot%3Bsatellites%26quot%3B%20you%20can%20collect%20to%20match%20with%20your%20planets%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Blabs%26quot%3B%20for%20users%20to%20pool%20their%20energy%20together%20to%20upgrade%20planets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20I%20wound%20up%20meeting%20the%20app's%20goal%20of%2010%2C000%20steps%20a%20day%2C%205%20days%20a%20week%2C%20it%20is%20one%20surprisingly%20complex%20step%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Peer%20pressure%20was%20a%20bigger%20motivator%20for%20me%20than%20the%20planets%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20Walkr%20planet%20collecting%20step%20counter%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6c77a912f290019aa3362%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EScreenshot%20of%20the%20game's%20co-pilot%20feature%2C%20and%20how%20energy%20is%20used%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20discovery%20of%20new%20planets%20in%20Walkr%3Cp%3EInsider%2FKai%20Xiang%20Teo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20I%20used%20Walkr%20and%20brought%20new%20friends%20into%20the%20planet-collecting%20fold%2C%20the%20more%20it%20became%20clear%20that%20the%20app%20is%20less%20about%20motivating%20you%20with%20gamification%20and%20more%20about%20pushing%20you%20with%20peer%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWalkr%20has%20a%20co-pilot%20feature%2C%20allowing%20your%20friends%20to%20gain%20some%20of%20the%20energy%20that%20you%20generate%20from%20walking%20%E2%80%94%20I%20added%20three%20close%20friends%20as%20co-pilots%20shortly%20after%20first%20downloading%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20created%20an%20interesting%20side%20effect%3A%20irate%20friends%20noticing%20I%20haven't%20been%20walking%20much%20lately%2C%20and%20who%20began%20badgering%20me%20to%20walk%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20worked%20both%20ways%20%E2%80%94%20I%20found%20myself%20pushing%20friends%20to%20walk%20more%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20You%20might%20not%20be%20into%20%26quot%3Bextrinsic%20motivation%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Punggol%20Park%2C%20Singapore%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6c8e14a32f3001974a6f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYes%2C%20I%20enjoy%20the%20exploring%20the%20great%20outdoors%2C%20but%20I'd%20enjoy%20it%20even%20more%20if%20I'm%20also%20collecting%20planets%20while%20I'm%20out%20there.%3Cp%3EInsider%2FKai%20Xiang%20Teo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20tried%20pitching%20the%20app%20to%20a%20friend%20to%20score%20another%20convert%20and%20potential%20co-pilot%2C%20he%20started%20at%20me%20blankly%20and%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3BWhy%20do%20you%20need%20planets%20to%20convince%20you%20to%20walk%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20explained%20to%20him%20that%20%E2%80%94%20as%20ridiculous%20as%20it%20might%20sound%20%E2%80%94%20I%20love%20structured%20playtime.%20Basically%2C%20I'm%20driven%20by%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Ftopics%2Fpsychology%2Fextrinsic-motivation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bextrinsic%20motivation%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20motivation%20that%20is%20driven%20by%20external%20rewards%20%E2%80%94%20like%20planets%2C%20points%2C%20or%20game%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20is%20a%20fan%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Ftopics%2Fsocial-sciences%2Fintrinsic-motivation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bintrinsic%20motivation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20does%20things%20because%20he%20enjoys%20the%20act%20of%20doing%20them.%20For%20him%2C%20walking%20is%20innately%20fun%20because%20he%20gets%20to%20be%20outdoors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I%20think%20this%20split%20in%20our%20opinions%20captures%20the%20essence%20of%20what%20makes%20gamification%20apps%20like%20Walkr%20right%20or%20wrong%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20enjoy%20walking%20probably%20didn't%20need%20Walkr's%20planets%20to%20begin%20with%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20a%20structured%20playtime%20enthusiast%20like%20me%2C%20you'll%20probably%20love%20gathering%20Walkr's%20quirky%20collection%20of%20planets%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourdesire%20CEO%20Wei-Fan%20Chen%20told%20Insider%20they're%20still%20working%20on%20making%20the%20Walkr%20app%20more%20user-friendly%20and%20enjoyable%20to%20use%2C%20and%20are%20taking%20inspiration%20from%20user%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanet-collecting-walking-step-counting-app-walkr-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693270269000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e6c73f912f290019aa3354%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplanet-collecting-walking-step-counting-app-walkr-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20adore%