0%94%20which%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usnews.com%2Feducation%2Fk12%2Fcalifornia%2Fdistricts%2Fchino-valley-unified-110856%23%3A~%3Atext%3DOverview%2520of%2520Chino%2520Valley%2520Unified%2C34%2520schools%2520and%252026%252C520%2520students.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2026%2C000%20students%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20voted%20last%20month%20to%20approve%20a%20%26quot%3Bparental%20notification%26quot%3B%20policy%20that%20requires%20teachers%20and%20school%20staff%20to%20alert%20parents%20if%20their%20kids%20want%20to%20use%20pronouns%2C%20names%2C%20or%20bathrooms%2C%20or%20join%20sports%20teams%2C%20that%20differ%20from%20their%20birth-assigned%20sex%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fcalifornia%2Fstory%2F2023-08-28%2Fcalifornia-sues-chino-school-district-transgender-notification-policy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECalifornia%20Attorney%20General%20Rob%20Bonta%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foag.ca.gov%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2Fattachments%2Fpress-docs%2F082723.Complaint.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiled%20a%20lawsuit%3C%2Fa%3E%20Monday%20against%20the%20district%20accusing%20it%20of%20unlawfully%20discriminating%20against%20transgender%20and%20nonbinary%20students.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Foag.ca.gov%2Fnews%2Fpress-releases%2Fattorney-general-bonta-announces-lawsuit-challenging-chino-valley-unified-school%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bonta's%20office%20wrote%20that%20the%20policy%20puts%20these%20students%20%26quot%3Bin%20danger%20of%20imminent%2C%20irreparable%20harm%20from%20the%20consequences%20of%20forced%20disclosures%26quot%3B%20which%20subject%20the%20students%20%26quot%3Bto%20disparate%20treatment%20and%20harassment%2C%20i