0people%20from%20very%20different%20walks%20of%20life%20bond%20over%20an%20idea.%20As%20Chaithanya%2C%20Nita%20and%20Rahul%20share%20the%20story%20of%20Yunikee%E2%80%99s%20inception%2C%20they%20are%20well%20aware%20of%20the%20incredible%20alignment%20of%20thoughts%2C%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20thanks%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Chaithanya.%20The%20trio%20was%20discussing%20the%20unfairness%20of%20the%20situation%20%E2%80%94%20how%20abled%20students%20had%20the%20privilege%20of%20continuing%20their%20schooling%20online%20while%20students%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145157%2Fahmedabad-ngo-proves-deaf-blindedness-doesnt-hinder-learning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehearing%20disabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20denied%20this%20basic%20right.%20They%20figured%20that%20this%20discrimination%20extended%20beyond%20the%20classroom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20if%20we%20were%20to%20start%20a%20platform%20that%20enabled%20hearing%20disabled%20people%20to%20access%20equal%20opportunities%20in%20terms%20of%20jobs%2C%20skillset%20training%20and%20more%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20thought.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20where%20it%20all%20started%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chaithanya%20shares.%20And%20there%20was%20no%20looking%20back.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EYunikee%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20an%20actual%20word%20(in%20Telugu)%20that%20translates%20to%20%E2%80%98I%20exist.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20me.%E2%80%99%E2%80%9D%20The%20reason%20for%20this%20stark%20reminder%20is%20that%2C%20unlike%20people%20of%20other%20disabilities%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F110922%2Fdeaflympics-deaf-athletes-2017%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeaf%20persons%3C%2Fa%3E%20cannot%20be%20identified%20unless%20one%20speaks%20to%20them%2C%20says%20Chaithanya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThrough%20Yunikee%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20an%20identity%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20trio%20dived%20deeper%20into%20the%20project%2C%20the%20most%20enthusiastic%20of%20them%20was%20Rahul.%20From%20personal%20experiences%2C%20Rahul%E2%80%99s%20views%20were%20cemented%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20people%20of%20his%20community%20were%20not%20given%20the%20right%20tools%20that%20they%20needed%20to%20excel.%20He%20shares%20that%20there%20were%20%E2%80%9Cclose%20to%20no%20learning%20platforms%20for%20deaf%20people%20at%20all%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYunikee%2C%20he%20says%2C%20addresses%20this%20gap%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F191729%2Fias-hero-upsc-exam-topper-saumya-sharma-hearing-impaired-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eempowering%20deaf%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20free%20themselves%20from%20the%20chokehold%20of%20dependency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20simply%20forced%20to%20continue%20our%20family%20business%20because%20of%20a%20lack%20of%20options%20in%20the%20job%20market.%20As%20someone%20who%20would%20scour%20the%20job%20market%20looking%20for%20jobs%2C%20and%20now%20as%20someone%20who%20is%20part%20of%20an%20initiative%20that%20trains%20deaf%20people%20to%20be%20adept%20at%20what%20they%20do%2C%20I%20have%20seen%20both%20ends%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rahul%20says.%20%E2%80%9CYunikee%20enables%20us%20to%20be%20independent.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCJdijPVj8c4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCJdijPVj8c4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_camp