india.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-300x186.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-500x310.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-768x477.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FIMG_1091_11zon-1692369236-150x93.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327708%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22698%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20kitchen%20garden%20at%20Woodway%20Heritage%20Bungalow%20boasts%20of%20a%20variety%20of%20produce%20and%20guests%20can%20also%20enjoy%20a%20barbeque%20on%20the%20land%20in%20the%20evenings%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Susmitha%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20the%20furniture%20is%20from%20the%20original%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20brass%20vessels%20that%20were%20used%20for%20cooking%20back%20in%20the%20day.%20Everything%20is%20designed%20around%20taking%20the%20guests%20back%20a%20100%20years%2C%20yet%20feeling%20luxurious%20in%20the%20same%20moment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20who%20thinks%20this%20is%20the%20main%20draw%20at%20Woodway%2C%20it%20gets%20better.%20The%20food%20is%20a%20completely%20different%20magic%20in%20itself.%20Susmitha%20says%20that%20the%20secret%20lies%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F286607%2Ffriends-quit-job-to-build-ecofriendly-home-stay-for-weekend-getaway-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20garden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20from%20where%20they%20source%20around%2070%20percent%20of%20their%20total%20produce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMother%20Nature%20provides%20us%20with%20colocasia%2C%20mushrooms%2C%20aubergines%2C%20jackfruits%2C%20horse%20gram%2C%20turmeric%20leaves%2C%20pomelo%2C%20red%20rice%