20I%20can%20speak%20English%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%2C%20noting%20that%20she%20aspires%20to%20be%20a%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiya%20is%20part%20of%20a%20cohort%20of%201%20lakh%20students%20under%20Muskaan%20Dreams%2C%20whose%20founder%20Abhishek%20Dubey%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20make%20learning%20in%20government%20schools%20fun.%20He%20does%20so%20through%20a%20number%20of%20interventions%2C%20including%20teaching%20children%20NCERT%20syllabus%20via%20animations%20and%20fun%20videos.%20The%20non-profit%20aims%20to%20bridge%20the%20digital%20gap%20in%20transforming%20education%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F178695%2Fbengaluru-tactile-books-graphics-education-disability-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emarginalised%20children%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20rural%20communities%20without%20the%20burden%20of%20an%20additional%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20has%20introduced%20a%20number%20of%20interventions%2C%20including%20teaching%20children%20NCERT%20syllabus%20via%20animations%20and%20fun%20videos.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2FMuskaan-Dreams-1-1692363836-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-327623%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20has%20introduced%20a%20number%20of%20interventions%2C%20including%20teaching%20children%20the%20NCERT%20syllabus%20via%20animations%20and%20fun%20videos.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20work%20on%20digital%20inclusion.%20Our%20focus%20is%20that%20every%20child%20should%20have%20digital%20%3Cem%3Eshiksha%20%3C%2Fem%3E(education)%20as%20technology%20is%20our%20future.%20If%20these%20students%20do%20not%20adapt%20to%20digital%20methods%2C%20chances%20are%20that%20they%20miss%20out%20on%20good%20opportunities.%20With%20Muskaan%20Dreams%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20bring%20smiles%20to%20these%20children%20and%20help%20them%20fulfil%20their%20dreams%20of%20a%20better%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%2031-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202017%2C%20the%20non-profit%20has%20so%20far%20collaborated%20with%201%2C000%20government%20schools%20across%20Maharashtra%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98When%20I%20took%20a%20stand%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20farmer%20family%20in%20rural%20Gwalior%2C%20Abhishek%20developed%20an%20interest%20in%20teaching%20underprivileged%20children%20during%20his%20college%20days.%20In%202013%2C%20while%20studying%20engineering%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20he%20started%20devoting%20his%20weekends%20to%20teaching%20children%20in%20government-run%20shelter%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20I%20saw%20one%20of%20my%20classmates%20going%20to%20teach%20students%20in%20shelter%20homes.%20I%20went%20along%20with%20her%20and%20saw%20how%20such%20children%20are%20deprived%20of%20education.%20Most%20of%20them%20are%20children%20of%20single%20parents%20and%20from%20tribal%20or%20rural%20backgrounds.%20Coming%20from%20a%20rural