%20in%20life%20%E2%80%94%20health.%20The%20blatant%20lies%20used%20by%20food%20companies%20in%20their%20packaging%20really%20bothers%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20this%20passion%20that%20led%20him%20to%20create%20the%20infamous%20viral%20video%20in%20April%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20label%20on%20that%20drink%20says%20that%20you%20get%20stronger%20bones%20and%20muscles.%20The%20reason%20I%20chose%20to%20make%20a%20video%20on%20this%20drink%20is%20because%20people%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F301227%2Fharvard-law-mba-grad-empower-underprivileged-kids-to-eat-healthy-through-games-foodshaala-foundation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeel%20this%20is%20healthy%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20no%20qualms%20about%20giving%20this%20twice%20a%20day%20to%20their%20children%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%2014%20times%20a%20week.%20People%20think%20aerated%20drinks%20like%20coke%20are%20unhealthy%2C%20which%20we%20may%20have%20only%20once%20a%20week.%20But%20the%20former%20has%20a%20direct%20impact%20on%20our%20health%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20Instagram%20%40foodpharmer%2C%20Revant%20educates%20about%20500%2C000%20of%20his%20followers%20on%20how%20they%20can%20make%20healthier%20choices.%20These%20include%20videos%20decoding%20labels%20of%20popular%20packaged%20noodles%2C%20drinks%2C%20biscuits%2C%20sauces%20and%20more%2C%20as%20well%20as%20helping%20people%20decide%20which%20bread%20is%20better%20for%20them%2C%20which%20drink%20they%20can%20choose%2C%20etc.%20He%20is%20also%20promoting%20small%20businesses%20that%20are%20%E2%80%9Crelatively%20healthier%E2%80%9D%20than%20the%20bigger%20brands.%20His%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20people%20choose%20better%2C%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ERemember%20this%20next%20time%20you%E2%80%99re%20at%20the%20supermarket%